{"type":"message","id":"ce8478cf","parentId":"1f4384ad","timestamp":"2026-06-29T09:18:14.976Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"A new session was started via /new or /reset. Execute your Session Startup sequence now - read the required files before responding to the user. If BOOTSTRAP.md exists in the provided Project Context, read it and follow its instructions first. Then greet the user in your configured persona, if one is provided. Be yourself - use your defined voice, mannerisms, and mood. Keep it to 1-3 sentences and ask what they want to do. If the runtime model differs from default_model in the system prompt, mention the default model. Do not mention internal steps, files, tools, or reasoning.\nCurrent time: Monday, June 29th, 2026 - 17:18 (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-06-29 09:18 UTC"}],"timestamp":1782724694972}}
{"type":"message","id":"56c82ad6","parentId":"ce8478cf","timestamp":"2026-06-29T09:18:25.528Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user has started a new session. I need to execute my Session Startup sequence:\n\n1. Read BOOTSTRAP.md if it exists (not mentioned in the project context)\n2. Read self-improving memory.md (HOT layer)\n3. Read proactivity/memory.md\n4. Read .learnings/ERRORS.md last 10 entries\n5. Check if runtime model differs from default_model\n\nLet me start by reading the required files per AGENTS.md instructions.\n\nThe runtime model is `sf/glm-5.2` and default_model is also `sf/glm-5.2`, so they match - no need to mention it.\n\nLet me check for BOOTSTRAP.md first and read the required files.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_w4tMxaNTSpyEKUjmDOTm9490","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\BOOTSTRAP.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_01_bz3HGgUCO9oawx5tPvUd5514","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\self-improving\\memory.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_02_Nk6HPmAwFljjcD623UO76259","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\proactivity\\memory.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_03_DLN2wq1eHUDgNNC1gyXX8104","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\.learnings\\ERRORS.md","limit":30}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"sf","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":17096,"output":381,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":17477,"cost":{"input":0.017096,"output":0.0012192000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0183152}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782724694982,"responseId":"cht000d8d30@dx19f12ac1eb3ba5c352"}}
{"type":"message","id":"4d3a364e","parentId":"56c82ad6","timestamp":"2026-06-29T09:18:25.655Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_w4tMxaNTSpyEKUjmDOTm9490","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"status\": \"error\",\n  \"tool\": \"read\",\n  \"error\": \"ENOENT: no such file or directory, access 'C:\\\\Users\\\\admin\\\\.openclaw\\\\agents\\\\dev-factory\\\\BOOTSTRAP.md'\"\n}"}],"details":{"status":"error","tool":"read","error":"ENOENT: no such file or directory, access 'C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\BOOTSTRAP.md'"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1782724705655}}
{"type":"message","id":"e6f13896","parentId":"4d3a364e","timestamp":"2026-06-29T09:18:25.655Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_01_bz3HGgUCO9oawx5tPvUd5514","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# self-improving memory\n\n## HOT Layer\n\n### 核心行为规则\n1. **所有代码修改直接执行** — 发现问题 → 用 edit/write 工具直接修改 → 验证\n2. **任何测试逻辑必须先完整读取CSV原文** — 列D方法+列E标准，不得自己推断或创造\n3. **E2E测试失败时先截图+分析HTML结构** — 确认选择器正确性后再重试，不要盲目试错\n4. **精确修复，禁止打补丁** — 发现问题必须找到根因，不是在表面打补丁\n5. **删除字段/变量前必须检查下游依赖** — grep 全项目，确认无引用后再删除（v7.113 教训）\n\n### 设备存储铁律（v7.17 教训）\n1. **设备标识必须使用 MAC 地址** — 禁止使用 IP 作为标识\n2. **MAC 格式统一**：无分隔符小写（如 `240f9b764193`）\n3. **SADP 发现必定返回有效 MAC** — 设备无 MAC 无法入网\n4. **存储路径**：`data/devices/{mac_clean}/`\n5. **禁止重复存储** — 同一设备只能有一个目录（按 MAC）\n\n### 禁止过度开发（v7.17 教训）\n1. **老板说禁止过度开发** = 停止开发，只做精简检查\n2. **不要新增功能** = 只修复问题\n3. **不要扩展修改范围** = 只改老板明确要求的\n\n### 备份三步法（v7.97 教训）⚠️ CRITICAL\n1. **创建**: 执行备份命令\n2. **验证**: `Test-Path` + 文件大小/数量确认\n3. **记录**: 写入 memory 文件（路径、内容、时间）\n- ❌ 不验证 = 没做备份\n\n### 版本号铁律（v7.97 教训）\n1. **constants.py 是唯一定义** — `VERSION` + `VERSION_NUM`\n2. **HEARTBEAT.md 从 constants.py 同步** — 不手动写版本号\n3. **每次代码修改后检查版本一致性**\n\n### WASM 与 ISAPI 完全独立（v7.97 教训）\n1. **PTZ 控制 → ISAPI** — 不依赖 WASM\n2. **视频播放 → WASM** — 需要 WebSocket 代理\n3. **可安全删除 WASM 而不影响 PTZ**\n4. **设备凭据从 device_config.py 读取** — 不硬编码 IP/密码\n\n### 搜索策略（v7.97 教训）\n1. **全量搜索优先** — 先 `Get-ChildItem -Recurse`，不要逐轮试路径\n2. **一轮到位** — 不要多轮猜测\n\n### 工作流\n- 发现问题 → 直接修复 → 验证 → 汇报结果\n- 被老板纠正 → 立即写入 corrections.md\n- 任务完成 → 验证修改 → 汇报结果\n- 备份操作 → 创建+验证+记录，三步缺一不可\n\n### 已知问题模式\n- 前端检测函数必须使用 `allDevices.find()` 获取凭据，不是 `connectedDevice`\n- P轴限位跳变判断：`abs(delta) > 1800`\n- 预置点10 在 function.py 的 _setup_home_preset() 设置，只设一次\n- ISAPI set_preset 正确用法：先 absolute_move 到位 → set_preset(id) 无坐标（v7.114 教训）\n- goto_home_and_wait 内置重试，调用方只做 `if not: return error`（v7.114 教训）\n- 刹车 = continuous_move(0,0,0)，ISAPI 标准停止操作（v7.114 教训）\n\n### 前端数据源（v7.54 教训）\n1. **function.json是主控台数据源** — console.html从opt_values读取填充下拉菜单\n2. **loadShutter/loadIris有动态加载逻辑** — loadExposure之前没有，导致空白\n3. **新增下拉菜单选项时同步更新updateXxxState** — 启用/禁用逻辑要匹配新选项\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1782724705655}}
