{"type":"message","id":"d05a1a79","parentId":"4dc81afc","timestamp":"2026-06-29T09:22:37.598Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see the root cause. Let me verify a few more things:\n\n1. The `/api/v1/discovery/sadp` endpoint returns 500 because `SADPManager()` can't find the `Sadp.dll` file.\n2. The DLL search paths are `SDK/hik/Sadp.dll` and `src/core/Sadp.dll`.\n3. Let me check what SDK files actually exist and where.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"找到根因了。让我确认文件状态。\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_j0vcorhfphghdyudqalni7hj","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub && Get-ChildItem -Recurse -Filter \"Sadp.dll\" -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | Select-Object FullName,Length,LastWriteTime"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_qzjqw597resgxausi5aly985","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub && Get-ChildItem SDK\\ -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | Select-Object Name,FullName"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ug8akf1ag5djjm43hb4katj5","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub && python -c \"from src.config_paths import SDK_LIBS_DIR; print(SDK_LIBS_DIR)\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"sf","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":42018,"output":333,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":42351,"cost":{"input":0.042018,"output":0.0010656,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0430836}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782724938233,"responseId":"cht000d425e@dx19f12afe702b85e322"}}
