{"type":"message","id":"4bf52504","parentId":"54e1efc8","timestamp":"2026-06-29T10:42:08.980Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_oDf5LYYWtopcG2naizxq2122","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"    def _modify_ip_via_sadp(self, sadp_dev, new_ip: str, subnet_mask: str,\r\n                             gateway: str, password: str) -> dict:\r\n        \"\"\"通过 SADP V40 DLL 修改 IP（官方 API，不绕开 DLL）。\r\n\r\n        流程:\r\n        1. 检测 IP 是否被占用 (PING)\r\n        2. 调用 SADP V40 DLL SADP_ModifyDeviceNetParam_V40\r\n        3. 查询错误码含义\r\n        4. 修改后等待 5 秒，验证新 IP 可达\r\n        \"\"\"\r\n        # P2.5: 判断 IP 是否被占用\r\n        if check_reachable(new_ip, timeout=2):\r\n            LOG.log(\"warning\", f\"目标 IP {new_ip} 已被占用，需更换 IP\")\r\n            return {\r\n                \"success\": False,\r\n                \"message\": f\"目标 IP {new_ip} 已被占用，请更换\",\r\n                \"error_code\": \"IP_CONFLICT\",\r\n            }\r\n\r\n        # 通过 SADP SDK DLL 修改网络参数（官方 API）\r\n        if SADP_DLL_AVAILABLE:\r\n            LOG.log(\"info\", f\"SADP DLL 修改 IP: MAC={sadp_dev.mac} -> {new_ip}\")\r\n            try:\r\n                mgr = SADPManagerDLL()\r\n                result = mgr.modify_device_network(\r\n                    mac=sadp_dev.mac,\r\n                    password=password,\r\n                    new_ip=new_ip,\r\n                    subnet_mask=subnet_mask,\r\n                    gateway=gateway,\r\n                    http_port=getattr(sadp_dev, 'http_port', 80),\r\n                )\r\n                if result.get(\"success\"):\r\n                    # 等待设备应用新 IP (P2.5: 10秒)\r\n                    LOG.log(\"info\", \"等待 10 秒让设备应用新 IP...\")\r\n                    time.sleep(3)\r\n                    if check_reachable(new_ip, timeout=3):\r\n                        sadp_dev.ip = new_ip\r\n                        sadp_dev.gateway = gateway\r\n                        sadp_dev.subnet_mask = subnet_mask\r\n                        self.config.upsert_device(sadp_dev.mac, {\r\n                            \"ip\": new_ip,\r\n                            \"model\": sadp_dev.model,\r\n                            \"mac\": sadp_dev.mac,\r\n                        })\r\n                        return {\r\n                            \"success\": True,\r\n                            \"message\": f\"IP 修改成功: {sadp_dev.ip} -> {new_ip}\",\r\n                            \"new_ip\": new_ip,\r\n                            \"method\": \"SADP_DLL\",\r\n                        }\r\n                    return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"IP 修改成功但 {new_ip} 不可达\"}\r\n                # DLL 返回错误\r\n                error_msg = result.get(\"message\", \"修改失败\")\r\n                LOG.log(\"error\", f\"SADP DLL 修改失败: {error_msg}\")\r\n                return {\r\n                    \"success\": False,\r\n                    \"message\": error_msg,\r\n                    \"method\": \"SADP_DLL\",\r\n                }\r\n            except Exception as e:\r\n                LOG.log(\"error\", f\"SADP DLL 修改 IP 异常: {e}\")\r\n                LOG.log(\"warning\", \"回退到备用方案（不可用）\")\r\n\r\n        # 回退方案: DLL 不可用时返回错误而非使用裸 socket\r\n        return {\r\n            \"success\": False,\r\n            \"message\": \"SADP DLL 不可用，无法修改 IP。请复制 Sadp.dll 到项目目录。\",\r\n        }\r\n\r\n\n[822 more lines in file. Use offset=1499 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1782729728980}}
{"type":"message","id":"dd877a2e","parentId":"4bf52504","timestamp":"2026-06-29T10:42:26.603Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"  response已完整梳理。汇报：\n\n---\n\n## 修改设备 IP 实现分析\n\n### 调用链\n\n```\nPOST /api/v1/sadp/{mac}/modify-ip  (router.py:716)\n  └─ PTZDeviceController.modify_reachable_with_retry()  (ptz_controller.py:1499)\n       ├─ P2.4: 检测原IP可达性 (PING)\n       ├─ P2.5: IP修改循环 (max 3次)\n       │   ├─ 检测目标IP被占用 → find_available_ip() 自动找空闲IP\n       │   ├─ SADP扫描确认设备在线\n       │   └─ PTZDeviceController._modify_ip_via_sadp()  (ptz_controller.py:1429)\n       │        └─ SADPManagerDLL.modify_device_network()  (sadp_discovery.py:1123)\n       │             ├─ SADP_Start_V40 注册回调\n       │             ├─ SendInquiry 触发设备广播\n       │             ├─ 等待设备出现在回调列表 (≤15s)\n       │             └─ SADP_ModifyDeviceNetParam_V40()  ← 核心 DLL API\n       │                  ├─ MAC + 密码 (cp936 + null终止)\n       │                  ├─ SADP_DEV_NET_PARAM (IP/掩码/网关/端口)\n       │                  └─ 返回 SADP_DEV_RET_NET_PARAM\n       └─ 验证: SADP重新扫描 → PING确认 → 保存到 PTZ_config.json\n```\n\n### 四步回答\n\n#### 1. 什么程序\n**Hikvision 官方 Sadp.dll (V40)** — SADP SDK 动态库，c 语言原生 DLL，通过 ctypes 调用。\n\n#### 2. 什么方法\n`SADP_ModifyDeviceNetParam_V40()` — 官方 DLL 导出函数，签名：\n```c\nBOOL SADP_ModifyDeviceNetParam_V40(\n    char* szMAC,                    // MAC地址 (小写横杠格式)\n    char* szPassword,               // 设备密码 (AES加密传输)\n    SADP_DEV_NET_PARAM* pstParam,  // 新网络参数结构体\n    SADP_DEV_RET_NET_PARAM* pstRet, // 返回参数\n    int dwRetSize                   // sizeof(返回结构体)\n);\n```\n- **MAC 格式**：小写+横杠 `24-0f-9b-76-41-93`\n- **密码编码**：`cp936 + null终止`（匹配C demo中 `strcpy()` 行为）\n- **传输加密**：DLL 内部 AES-128-ECB 加密密码，依赖 `libcrypto-1_1.dll` / `libssl-1_1.dll`\n\n#### 3. 跨网段实现机制\n\n**SADP 协议本质 = 二层多播**，不依赖 IP 层路由：\n\n```\nSADP_ModifyDeviceNetParam_V40 跨网段工作流程：\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│ SADP DLL (本机)                                      │\n│   ├─ 通过 NPF 驱动直接操作网卡 (数据链路层)            │\n│   ├─ 发送 SADP 多播包 → 239.255.255.250:37020        │\n│   │   (二层广播帧，不经过IP路由)                       │\n│   ├─ 设备监听多播端口，收到修改指令                     │\n│   └─ 设备内部修改 IP → 重启网络栈 → 新IP生效          │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n**关键点**：\n- SADP 走**二层多播**（MAC 层广播），不依赖 IP 路由\n- 只要设备在同一广播域（同一 VLAN / 交换机），无论 IP 是否可达都能修改\n- 这也是为什么 `P2.4` 检测到 IP 不可达后仍能继续修改\n- 修改前通过 `SendInquiry` 激活设备（类似 ARP），确保 DLL 内部设备表中有该设备\n\n**限制**：\n- ❌ 不能跨 VLAN（二层广播域限制）\n- ❌ 不能跨路由器/NAT\n- ✅ 同广播域内任意 IP（即使不在同一子网）均可修改","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"sf","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":55931,"output":982,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":56913,"cost":{"input":0.055930999999999995,"output":0.0031424000000000005,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0590734}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782729728981,"responseId":"cht000de930@dx19f12f8e5f5b894652"}}
