{"type":"message","id":"2361f8ed","parentId":"2a1873b4","timestamp":"2026-06-29T11:26:33.596Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking why I stopped without giving feedback. I was in the middle of analyzing the SADP IP modification implementation when the conversation was interrupted. Let me compile and present the analysis I was working on.\n\nLet me summarize what I found about the IP modification implementation.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"抱歉老板，分析已完成，汇总如下：\n\n---\n\n## AstroHub 修改设备 IP 实现分析\n\n### 调用链\n\n```\nPOST /api/v1/sadp/{mac}/modify-ip  (router.py:716)\n  → PTZDeviceController.modify_reachable_with_retry()  (ptz_controller.py:1499)\n    → PTZDeviceController._modify_ip_via_sadp()  (ptz_controller.py:1429)\n      → SADPManagerDLL.modify_device_network()  (sadp_discovery.py:1123)\n        → SADP_ModifyDeviceNetParam_V40 (Sadp.dll C 函数)\n```\n\n### 核心方法\n\n| 层级 | 文件 | 职责 |\n|------|------|------|\n| **Router** | `router.py:716` | 接收 HTTP 请求，转发给 PTZDeviceController |\n| **Orchestrator** | `ptz_controller.py:1499` | 可达性判断 → 重试循环 → SADP扫描确认 → 配置持久化 |\n| **Executor** | `ptz_controller.py:1429` | 检查 IP 冲突 → 调用 SADP DLL |\n| **DLL Wrapper** | `sadp_discovery.py:1123` | ctypes 封装 Sadp.dll 的 `SADP_ModifyDeviceNetParam_V40` |\n\n### 跨网段原理\n\nSADP 协议工作在**链路层**（多播 `239.255.255.250:37020`），不依赖 IP 层路由：\n\n```\n本机 ──(多播/UDP)──→ 局域网所有海康设备\n                         ↑\n                    设备收到后回复自己的 MAC/IP/掩码/网关\n```\n\n`SADP_ModifyDeviceNetParam_V40` 直接写入设备的网络参数（IP/掩码/网关），**不需要设备当前 IP 与本机同网段**。只要设备在同一个二层广播域内（同一交换机/VLAN），SADP 就能发现并修改它。\n\n### 完整流程（P2.4 → P2.5 → P2.6）\n\n```\n1. 可达性判断 (P2.4): PING 原 IP\n2. IP 冲突检测: PING 目标 IP，冲突则自动找可用 IP (.64 起扫描)\n3. SADP 扫描: 确认设备在回调列表中\n4. DLL 调用: SADP_ModifyDeviceNetParam_V40(mac, password, net_param)\n5. 等待 10s → 重新 SADP 扫描确认新 IP\n6. 配置持久化 (P2.6): upsert_device 写入 PTZ_config.json\n7. 最多重试 3 次\n```\n\n---\n\n有什么需要调整的？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"sf","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":56048,"output":672,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":56720,"cost":{"input":0.056048,"output":0.0021504000000000002,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0581984}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782732367389,"responseId":"cht000db351@dx19f13212cdeb894652"}}
