{"type":"message","id":"e25ff54b","parentId":"229014a7","timestamp":"2026-06-29T11:32:08.547Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me trace the full picture. The user is asking why PTZ device gateway is not showing. Let me check:\n\n1. The `/api/v1/devices` endpoint - what does it return for gateway?\n2. The `list_stored_devices()` method - what does it return?\n3. The manual add flow - does it save gateway?\n\nLet me trace the flow more carefully.\n\nFrom the API response I got earlier:\n```json\n{\"success\":true,\"data\":[{\"mac\":\"240f9b764193\",\"ip\":\"192.168.5.72\",\"name\":\"4k 32X DC\",\"model\":\"iDS-2DF8C832IXS-A\",\"gateway\":\"192.168.5.1\",\"subnet_mask\":\"255.255.255.0\",\"source\":\"merged\",\"online\":true,\"activated\":true,\"has_credentials\":true}],\"total\":1}\n```\n\nGateway IS returned: `\"gateway\":\"192.168.5.1\"`\n\nSo the API has it. The frontend renders `d.gateway || '--'`. So it should show.\n\nLet me check the device data file and see what's stored, and also check the manual add flow more carefully.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_lk808hbvfrv24pflab5q58oj","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":60,"offset":517,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\api\\router.py"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_l9trt249yq1tg14y36mnzs7l","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub && Get-ChildItem data\\devices\\ -Recurse -Filter \"*.json\" | Select-Object FullName,Length | Format-Table -AutoSize"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"sf","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":69656,"output":435,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":70091,"cost":{"input":0.069656,"output":0.0013920000000000002,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.071048}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782732715531,"responseId":"cht000d2196@dx19f1326780db958312"}}
{"type":"message","id":"6959558b","parentId":"e25ff54b","timestamp":"2026-06-29T11:32:09.063Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_lk808hbvfrv24pflab5q58oj","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"async def register_device(req: AddDeviceRequest) -> dict:\r\n    \"\"\"手动添加设备（IP + 凭据）并自动设为活跃。\r\n    \r\n    v7.17: 必须有 MAC 地址才能注册，如果没有则从 SADP 发现中查找。\r\n    \"\"\"\r\n    mgr: PTZDeviceController | None = _managers.get(\"ptz_controller\")  # type: ignore[assignment]\r\n    if not mgr:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": \"PTZDeviceController未初始化\"}\r\n    \r\n    # v7.17: 如果没有 MAC，从 SADP 发现中查找\r\n    device_mac = req.mac\r\n    device_model = req.model\r\n    device_name = req.name\r\n    \r\n    if not device_mac:\r\n        # 检查 SADP 发现中是否有该 IP 的设备\r\n        sadp_devices = mgr._discovered\r\n        for mac, info in sadp_devices.items():\r\n            if info.ip == req.ip:\r\n                device_mac = mac\r\n                device_model = device_model or getattr(info, 'model',PTZDeviceController | None)\r\n                device_name = device_name or getattr(info, 'device_name',PTZDeviceController | None)\r\n                break\r\n        \r\n        if not device_mac:\r\n            return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"未发现设备 {req.ip}，请先执行 SADP 发现\"}\r\n\r\n    # 使用正确的 MAC 保存\r\n    mgr.save_credentials(\r\n        ip=req.ip,\r\n        username=req.username,\r\n        password=req.password,\r\n        port=req.port,\r\n        mac=device_mac,  # v7.17: 必须使用真实 MAC\r\n        model=device_model,\r\n        name=device_name,\r\n    )\r\n\r\n    # 注册到 DeviceManager\r\n    dm: DeviceManager | None = _managers.get(\"device_manager\")  # type: ignore[assignment]\r\n    if dm:\r\n        dm.register_device(\r\n            mac=device_mac,  # v7.17: 使用真实 MAC\r\n            ip=req.ip,\r\n            name=device_name or f\"PTZ-{req.ip}\",\r\n            model=device_model or \"PTZ\",\r\n        )\r\n    \r\n    # 设为活跃设备（更新 registry.json）\r\n    mgr.config.upsert_device(device_mac, {\"ip\": req.ip, \"model\": device_model or \"\", \"port\": req.port, \"mac\": device_mac})\r\n\r\n    log_info(\"device\", \"register\", {\"ip\": req.ip, \"mac\": device_mac, \"name\": device_name})\r\n    return {\r\n        \"success\": True,\r\n        \"message\": f\"设备已保存: {device_mac} @ {req.ip}\",\r\n        \"device\": {\r\n            \"ip\": req.ip,\r\n            \"port\": req.port,\r\n            \"name\": device_name,\r\n            \"model\": device_model,\r\n\n[3065 more lines in file. Use offset=577 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1782732729063}}
