{"type":"message","id":"a812eba0","parentId":"966acff5","timestamp":"2026-06-30T12:41:14.431Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"老板让我继续检查速度测试的ZOOM分组显示问题。我已经发现了：\n\n1. 后端speed.py确实有ZOOM测试逻辑（zoom_levels = [zoom_min, zoom_mid, zoom_max]）\n2. 后端返回的all_results包含zoom字段\n3. router.py有个_format_speed_results函数，从搜索结果看它返回speed_map, pan_speed, tilt_speed, by_zoom等\n4. 前端advanced.html只显示pan_speed和tilt_speed，没有显示by_zoom\n\n让我继续检查router.py中的_format_speed_results函数，看看它是如何处理数据的，以及是否正确包含了zoom分组信息。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"继续检查router.py中的 `_format_speed_results` 函数，看它如何处理数据："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-afafc4c31d0348bd9c2172bfeaa1ef25","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":60,"offset":2282,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\api\\router.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":86887,"output":197,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":87084,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782823252926,"responseId":"cht000d3f94@dx19f188bff672872503"}}
{"type":"message","id":"2f5dbe35","parentId":"a812eba0","timestamp":"2026-06-30T12:41:14.464Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool-afafc4c31d0348bd9c2172bfeaa1ef25","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"def _format_speed_results(results: list) -> dict:\r\n    \"\"\"将 run_all_tests 返回的 list 分组为前端格式。\r\n    \r\n    Returns: {speed_map, pan_speed, tilt_speed, by_zoom, total_tests}\r\n    \"\"\"\r\n    by_zoom = {}\r\n    speed_map = {}\r\n    pan_map = {}\r\n    tilt_map = {}\r\n    for r in results:\r\n        sl = str(r.get(\"speed_level\", 0))\r\n        sv = r.get(\"speed_val\", 0.0)\r\n        axis = r.get(\"axis\", \"\")\r\n        zoom = r.get(\"zoom\", 0)\r\n        speed_map.setdefault(sl, []).append(sv)\r\n        if axis == \"pan\":\r\n            pan_map.setdefault(sl, []).append(sv)\r\n        elif axis == \"tilt\":\r\n            tilt_map.setdefault(sl, []).append(sv)\r\n        by_zoom.setdefault(zoom, {}).setdefault(axis, {})[sl] = sv\r\n    for m in (speed_map, pan_map, tilt_map):\r\n        for k, v in m.items():\r\n            m[k] = round(sum(v) / len(v), 2)\r\n    return {\r\n        \"speed_map\": speed_map,\r\n        \"pan_speed\": pan_map,\r\n        \"tilt_speed\": tilt_map,\r\n        \"by_zoom\": by_zoom,\r\n        \"total_tests\": len(results),\r\n    }\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n@api_router.post(\"/advanced/detect/start\", summary=\"启动一键检测\", tags=[\"Advanced\"])\r\nasync def advanced_detect_start(req: AdvancedDetectStartRequest) -> dict:\r\n    \"\"\"启动异步一键检测 (Function + Limit + Speed)。\"\"\"\r\n    import asyncio\r\n    import uuid\r\n\r\n    task_id = str(uuid.uuid4())\r\n    detect_tasks[task_id] = {\r\n        \"status\": \"running\",\r\n        \"progress\": 0.0,\r\n        \"current_step\": \"initializing\",\r\n        \"results\": {},\r\n        \"items\": req.items,\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    async def _run_detect():\r\n        try:\r\n            from src.ptz.isapi.client import ISAPIClient\r\n            from src.advanced.config_writer import write_device_config\r\n\r\n            def _cancelled():\r\n                return detect_tasks.get(task_id, {}).get(\"status\") == \"cancelled\"\r\n\r\n            mgr: PTZDeviceController | None = _managers.get(\"ptz_controller\")\r\n            if not mgr:\r\n                detect_tasks[task_id].update(status=\"failed\", current_step=\"PTZDeviceControllernot initialized\")\r\n                return\r\n\n[1302 more lines in file. Use offset=2342 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1782823274464}}
{"type":"message","id":"c70179a4","parentId":"2f5dbe35","timestamp":"2026-06-30T12:41:54.022Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，现在我看到了 `_format_speed_results` 函数。它返回：\n- speed_map: 按 speed_level 分组的速度值\n- pan_speed: 按 speed_level 分组的 Pan 速度\n- tilt_speed: 按 speed_level 分组的 Tilt 速度\n- by_zoom: 按 zoom 分组的数据，格式是 {zoom: {axis: {speed_level: value}}}\n\n所以后端确实返回了 `by_zoom` 字段！\n\n但前端 advanced.html 只显示了 `pan_speed` 和 `tilt_speed`，没有显示 `by_zoom`（ZOOM分组）。\n\n这就是问题所在！前端渲染逻辑需要修改，添加 ZOOM 分组的显示。\n\n让我总结一下问题：\n1. 后端正确返回了 `by_zoom` 字段，包含按 zoom 分组的速度数据\n2. 前端只显示 `pan_speed` 和 `tilt_speed`，忽略了 `by_zoom`\n3. 所以用户看不到 ZOOM 分组的结果\n\n修复方案：在前端 advanced.html 中添加 ZOOM 分组的显示逻辑。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"找到根因了！后端 `_format_speed_results` 函数正确返回了 `by_zoom` 字段，但**前端没有使用它**。\n\n---\n\n## 问题分析\n\n### 后端 (router.py:2282-2308)\n```python\ndef _format_speed_results(results: list) -> dict:\n    return {\n        \"speed_map\": speed_map,\n        \"pan_speed\": pan_map,\n        \"tilt_speed\": tilt_map,\n        \"by_zoom\": by_zoom,      # ✅ 已生成\n        \"total_tests\": len(results),\n    }\n```\n\n### 前端 (advanced.html:401-423)\n```javascript\nconst panSpeed = results.pan_speed || {};\nconst tiltSpeed = results.tilt_speed || {};\n// ❌ 完全没用到 by_zoom!\nfor (const level of allLevels) {\n    html += '<td>' + panSpeed[level] + '</td>';   // 只有Pan/Tilt\n    html += '<td>' + tiltSpeed[level] + '</td>';\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 修复方案\n\n前端需要添加 ZOOM 分组显示。修改 `src/web/includes/advanced.html`，在速度测试表格后添加 ZOOM 分组表格："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_0e7c45cb7cd1c94d87f1f5e3","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":30,"offset":410,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\includes\\advanced.html"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":110108,"output":662,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":110770,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782823274465,"responseId":"cht000d5973@dx19f188c56912871503"}}
{"type":"message","id":"c181df9a","parentId":"c70179a4","timestamp":"2026-06-30T12:41:54.056Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_0e7c45cb7cd1c94d87f1f5e3","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"        // Speed table\r\n        if (results.pan_speed || results.tilt_speed) {\r\n            html += '<table style=\"width:100%;font-size:11px;border-collapse:collapse;margin-top:8px\">';\r\n            html += '<tr style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #30363d\"><th style=\"text-align:left;padding:4px\">速度档位</th><th style=\"text-align:center;padding:4px\">Pan (°/s)</th><th style=\"text-align:right;padding:4px\">Tilt (°/s)</th></tr>';\r\n            \r\n            const panSpeed = results.pan_speed || {};\r\n            const tiltSpeed = results.tilt_speed || {};\r\n            const allLevels = new Set([...Object.keys(panSpeed), ...Object.keys(tiltSpeed)]);\r\n            \r\n            for (const level of Array.from(allLevels).sort((a,b) => a - b)) {\r\n                html += '<tr style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #21262d\">';\r\n                html += '<td style=\"padding:4px\">' + level + '</td>';\r\n                html += '<td style=\"text-align:center;padding:4px\">' + (panSpeed[level] || '-') + '</td>';\r\n                html += '<td style=\"text-align:right;padding:4px\">' + (tiltSpeed[level] || '-') + '</td>';\r\n                html += '</tr>';\r\n            }\r\n            html += '</table>';\r\n        }\r\n        html += '</div>';\r\n        resultEl.innerHTML = html;\r\n    } else {\r\n        // 功能测试结果\r\n        let html = '<table style=\"width:100%;font-size:11px;border-collapse:collapse\">';\r\n        html += '<tr style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #30363d\"><th style=\"text-align:left;padding:4px\">项目</th><th style=\"text-align:center;padding:4px\">支持</th><th style=\"text-align:right;padding:4px\">范围</th></tr>';\r\n\r\n        for (const [key, val] of Object.entries(results)) {\r\n            if (typeof val === 'object' && val !== null) {\r\n                const label = val.label || key;\r\n                const supported = val.supported ? 'Y' : 'N';\r\n                // v7.52: 兼容两种字段名：min/min_val, max/max_val\r\n\n[420 more lines in file. Use offset=440 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1782823314056}}
