{"type":"message","id":"1ea3a494","parentId":"0df6459b","timestamp":"2026-06-30T16:05:32.654Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool-dec723ca3dd349ff99cfd4bbcb372c1c","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\"\"\"\r\nAstroHub v2.0 - 统一路由聚合\r\n\r\n整合 M1-M11 所有模块路由到 /api/v1/ 下:\r\n- /api/v1/health            - 全局健康检查\r\n- /api/v1/discovery/sadp    - SADP 设备发现\r\n- /api/v1/devices/*         - 设备管理(真实)\r\n- /api/v1/ptz/*             - PTZ 控制(真实)\r\n- /api/v1/streams/*         - 流服务\r\n- /api/v1/calibration/*     - 校准\r\n- /api/v1/ascom/*           - ASCOM 设备\r\n- /api/v1/settings          - 系统设置\r\n\r\nAuthor: 雅痞张@南方天文\r\n\"\"\"\r\n\r\nfrom __future__ import annotations\r\n\r\nimport time\r\nfrom datetime import datetime, timezone\r\nfrom typing import Any\r\n\r\nfrom pydantic import BaseModel\r\nfrom fastapi import APIRouter, FastAPI, Query\r\nfrom fastapi.responses import JSONResponse, Response\r\n\r\n# v6.40: 操作日志\r\nfrom src.operation_logger import log_api, log_web, log_error, log_info\r\n\r\n# ================================================================ #\r\n\n[3560 more lines in file. Use offset=31 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1782835532654}}
{"type":"message","id":"ca30dee0","parentId":"1ea3a494","timestamp":"2026-06-30T16:06:15.740Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我看到router.py的顶部导入部分。我需要添加：\n1. `from concurrent.futures import ThreadPoolExecutor` - 用于并行ping\n2. 导入或使用check_reachable函数\n\n但为了最小改动，我可以直接在刷新API函数中导入这些，避免修改全局导入。\n\n让我在list_devices()函数之后添加刷新API函数。刷新API的逻辑：\n\n```python\n@api_router.post(\"/devices/refresh\", summary=\"刷新设备状态\", tags=[\"Devices\"])\nasync def refresh_devices() -> dict:\n    \"\"\"并行ping所有设备，更新在线状态。\"\"\"\n    from concurrent.futures import ThreadPoolExecutor\n    from src.core.ptz_controller import check_reachable\n    \n    mgr = _managers.get(\"ptz_controller\")\n    if not mgr:\n        return {\"success\": False, \"data\": [], \"total\": 0}\n    \n    # 获取设备列表（使用简化后的逻辑）\n    # ... (类似list_devices的逻辑)\n    \n    # 并行ping\n    devices_list = list(devices.values())\n    with ThreadPoolExecutor(max_workers=10) as executor:\n        results = executor.map(lambda ip: check_reachable(ip, timeout=1), [d[\"ip\"] for d in devices_list])\n    \n    # 更新状态\n    for dev, reachable in zip(devices_list, results):\n        if reachable:\n            dev[\"status\"] = \"在线\"\n        else:\n            dev[\"status\"] = \"离线\"\n    \n    return {\"success\": True, \"data\": devices_list, \"total\": len(devices_list)}\n```\n\n等等，我需要考虑一下：\n1. 刷新API应该复用list_devices的逻辑来获取设备列表\n2. 或者直接调用list_devices获取数据，然后再ping\n\n更简单的方式：\n- 先获取设备列表（调用内部逻辑）\n- 然后并行ping\n- 返回带状态的列表\n\n让我编写这个函数并插入到router.py中。\n\n但是有个问题：list_devices已经是async函数，我需要在refresh_devices中复用它的逻辑。\n\n最简单的方式是直接在refresh_devices中复制list_devices的设备获取逻辑，然后添加ping部分。\n\n或者我可以定义一个内部函数_get_devices_dict()来获取设备字典，然后两个API都调用它。\n\n为了最小改动，我选择：直接在refresh_devices中写完整的逻辑（获取设备 + ping）。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"现在添加刷新API。为了最小改动，我直接在list_devices()之后添加新函数，复用设备获取逻辑并添加并行ping："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-3056c16187674bbfae8f714f36fa6c76","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"    return {\"success\": True, \"data\": list(devices.values()), \"total\": len(devices)}\n\n\n@api_router.post(\"/devices/refresh\", summary=\"刷新设备状态\", tags=[\"Devices\"])\nasync def refresh_devices() -> dict:\n    \"\"\"并行ping所有设备，更新在线状态（timeout=1s）。\"\"\" \n    from concurrent.futures import ThreadPoolExecutor\n    from src.core.ptz_controller import check_reachable\n    \n    mgr: PTZDeviceController | None = _managers.get(\"ptz_controller\")\n    if not mgr:\n        return {\"success\": False, \"data\": [], \"total\": 0}\n\n    def _normalize_mac(mac: str) -> str:\n        import re\n        clean = mac.replace(\":\", \"\").replace(\"-\", \"\").lower()\n        if len(clean) != 12 or not re.match(r'^[0-9a-f]{12}$', clean):\n            return \"\"\n        return clean\n\n    stored = mgr.list_stored_devices()\n    discovered = mgr.get_discovered_devices()\n\n    # 以MAC为唯一键\n    devices: dict[str, dict[str, Any]] = {}\n    for dev in stored:\n        mac = _normalize_mac(dev.get(\"mac\", \"\") or \"\")\n        if mac:\n            devices[mac] = {\n                \"mac\": mac,\n                \"ip\": dev.get(\"ip\", \"\"),\n                \"name\": dev.get(\"name\", \"\") or dev.get(\"device_name\", \"\"),\n                \"model\": dev.get(\"model\", \"\"),\n                \"gateway\": dev.get(\"gateway\", \"\"),\n                \"subnet_mask\": dev.get(\"subnet_mask\", \"\"),\n                \"has_credentials\": True,\n                \"status\": \"离线\",\n            }\n\n    for sadp in discovered:\n        mac = _normalize_mac(sadp.get(\"mac\", \"\") or \"\")\n        if not mac:\n            continue\n        if mac in devices:\n            devices[mac][\"ip\"] = sadp.get(\"ip\", \"\") or devices[mac][\"ip\"]\n            devices[mac][\"model\"] = sadp.get(\"model\", \"\") or devices[mac][\"model\"]\n            devices[mac][\"gateway\"] = sadp.get(\"gateway\", \"\")\n            devices[mac][\"subnet_mask\"] = sadp.get(\"subnet_mask\", \"\")\n        else:\n            devices[mac] = {\n                \"mac\": mac,\n                \"ip\": sadp.get(\"ip\", \"\"),\n                \"name\": sadp.get(\"device_name\", \"\") or sadp.get(\"name\", \"\"),\n                \"model\": sadp.get(\"model\", \"\") or \"PTZ\",\n                \"gateway\": sadp.get(\"gateway\", \"\"),\n                \"subnet_mask\": sadp.get(\"subnet_mask\", \"\"),\n                \"has_credentials\": False,\n                \"status\": \"离线\",\n            }\n\n    # 并行ping检测状态\n    devices_list = list(devices.values())\n    ips = [d[\"ip\"] for d in devices_list if d[\"ip\"]]\n    \n    with ThreadPoolExecutor(max_workers=10) as executor:\n        reachability = list(executor.map(lambda ip: check_reachable(ip, timeout=1), ips))\n    \n    # 更新状态\n    ip_status = dict(zip(ips, reachability))\n    for dev in devices_list:\n        ip = dev.get(\"ip\", \"\")\n        if ip and ip_status.get(ip, False):\n            dev[\"status\"] = \"在线\"\n        else:\n            dev[\"status\"] = \"离线\"\n    \n    # 检查已连接状态\n    online_ips = mgr.list_controllers()\n    for dev in devices_list:\n        if dev.get(\"ip\") in online_ips and dev.get(\"status\") == \"在线\":\n            dev[\"status\"] = \"已连接\"\n\n    return {\"success\": True, \"data\": devices_list, \"total\": len(devices_list)}\n\n\n@api_router.post(\"/devices/active\", summary=\"设置上次连接的设备\", tags=[\"Devices\"])","oldText":"    return {\"success\": True, \"data\": list(devices.values()), \"total\": len(devices)}\n\n\n@api_router.post(\"/devices/active\", summary=\"设置上次连接的设备\", tags=[\"Devices\"])"}],"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\api\\router.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":105514,"output":1577,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":107091,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782835532656,"responseId":"cht000d5768@dx19f194761b3