{"type":"message","id":"97b742af","parentId":"4833ccf2","timestamp":"2026-06-30T16:15:31.896Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我找到了renderDevices和refreshDevices函数的位置。让我读取这些函数的完整内容，然后修改它们：\n\n1. refreshDevices() - 第1176行开始\n2. renderDevices() - 第1202行开始\n3. sourceBadge相关代码在第1210-1218行\n\n我需要：\n1. 修改refreshDevices()调用新的API\n2. 修改renderDevices()删除sourceBadge渲染\n3. 删除setInterval(refreshDevices, 15000)自动刷新逻辑（因为现在改为手动点击刷新）\n\n让我先读取这些函数的内容。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"好的，我找到了这些函数的位置。让我读取完整的函数内容，然后进行修改："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_62bffde3f6052f2b05a408f7","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":50,"offset":1176,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\index.html"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":145709,"output":218,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":145927,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782836113987,"responseId":"cht000d7557@dx19f1950471229bb503"}}
{"type":"message","id":"d3202e8f","parentId":"97b742af","timestamp":"2026-06-30T16:15:31.930Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_62bffde3f6052f2b05a408f7","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"        function refreshDevices() {\r\n            console.log('[REFRESH] refreshDevices called');\r\n            return apiGet('/api/v1/devices').then(function(result) {\r\n                console.log('[REFRESH] API response:', result);\r\n                if (!result.success) {\r\n                    allDevices = [];\r\n                    renderDevices([]);\r\n                    return;\r\n                }\r\n                allDevices = result.data || [];\r\n                renderDevices(allDevices);\r\n                // Update dashboard counters\r\n                var online = allDevices.filter(function(d) { return d.online; }).length;\r\n                var countEl = document.getElementById('devCount');\r\n                if (countEl) countEl.textContent = allDevices.length;\r\n                var onlineEl = document.getElementById('devOnline');\r\n                if (onlineEl) onlineEl.textContent = online;\r\n                var totalEl = document.getElementById('devTotal');\r\n                if (totalEl) totalEl.textContent = allDevices.length;\r\n                // Update PTZ & advanced device dropdowns\r\n                refreshPtzDeviceList();\r\n                refreshAdvancedDeviceSelectors();\r\n            }).catch(function(e) {\r\n                console.warn('Failed to refresh devices:', e);\r\n            });\r\n        }\r\n        function renderDevices(devices) {\r\n            var tb = document.getElementById('deviceTable');\r\n            if (!tb) return;\r\n            if (!devices.length) {\r\n                tb.innerHTML = '<tr><td colspan=\"8\" style=\"text-align:center;color:#6e7681\">暂无设备</td></tr>';\r\n                return;\r\n            }\r\n            var html = devices.map(function(d) {\r\n                var sourceBadge = d.source === 'sadp'\r\n                    ? '<span class=\"badge sadp\">SADP</span>'\r\n                    : '<span class=\"badge manual\">手动</span>';\r\n                var onlineBadge = d.online\r\n                    ? '<span class=\"badge online\">在线</span>'\r\n                    : '<span class=\"badge offline\">离线</span>';\r\n                var actions = buildDeviceActions(d);\r\n                return '<tr>'\r\n                    + '<td>' + sourceBadge + '</td>'\r\n                    + '<td>' + (d.mac || '--') + '</td>'\r\n                    + '<td>' + (d.ip || '--') + '</td>'\r\n                    + '<td>' + (d.gateway || '--') + '</td>'\r\n                    + '<td>' + (d.name || d.device_name || '--') + '</td>'\r\n                    + '<td>' + (d.model || '--') + '</td>'\r\n                    + '<td>' + onlineBadge + '</td>'\r\n                    + '<td>' + actions + '</td>'\r\n\n[1648 more lines in file. Use offset=1226 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1782836131930}}
{"type":"message","id":"6ce4fe7b","parentId":"d3202e8f","timestamp":"2026-06-30T16:16:05.425Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我看到了refreshDevices()和renderDevices()函数的完整内容。\n\n需要修改的内容：\n\n1. refreshDevices()函数：\n   - 当前调用GET /api/v1/devices\n   - 需要改成调用POST /api/v1/devices/refresh（这个API会ping设备并返回状态）\n   - 或者保持原有逻辑，但页面加载时异步调用refresh API\n   \n   但是老板说：\n   - 页面加载时获取设备列表（无状态）\n   - 异步调用refresh API获取状态\n   - 之后不需要ping，除非用户手动点击刷新\n\n   所以逻辑应该是：\n   - 页面加载时：调用GET /api/v1/devices（无状态）\n   - 异步调用POST /api/v1/devices/refresh（获取状态）\n   - 用户点击刷新按钮：调用POST /api/v1/devices/refresh\n\n2. renderDevices()函数：\n   - 删除sourceBadge相关代码（第1206-1208行）\n   - 删除'<td>' + sourceBadge + '</td>'这行（第1218行）\n   - 修改onlineBadge为状态显示（使用d.status而不是d.online）\n   - 修改colspan从8改成7（因为删除了一列）\n\n让我修改这些函数。\n\n首先修改renderDevices()函数：\n- 删除sourceBadge定义和使用\n- 修改online状态显示（使用d.status）\n- 修改colspan","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"好的，我看到了这两个函数的完整内容。现在需要修改：\n\n1. **refreshDevices()** - 调用新的refresh API\n2. **renderDevices()** - 删除sourceBadge渲染，改用status字段\n\n让我开始修改：\n\n第一步：修改renderDevices()函数，删除sourceBadge，使用status字段"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-b465fd8b939f4f36aa5900f349f07f37","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"        function renderDevices(devices) {\n            var tb = document.getElementById('deviceTable');\n            if (!tb) return;\n            if (!devices.length) {\n                tb.innerHTML = '<tr><td colspan=\"7\" style=\"text-align:center;color:#6e7681\">暂无设备</td></tr>'; \n                return;\n            }\n            var html = devices.map(function(d) {\n                var statusBadge = d.status === '已连接'\n                    ? '<span class=\"badge online\">已连接</span>'\n                    : (d.status === '在线'\n                        ? '<span class=\"badge online\">在线</span>'\n                        : '<span class=\"badge offline\">离线</span>');\n                var actions = buildDeviceActions(d);\n                return '<tr>'\n                    + '<td>' + (d.mac || '--') + '</td>'\n                    + '<td>' + (d.ip || '--') + '</td>' \n                    + '<td>' + (d.gateway || '--') + '</td>' \n                    + '<td>' + (d.name || d.device_name || '--') + '</td>'\n                    + '<td>' + (d.model || '--') + '</td>' \n                    + '<td>' + statusBadge + '</td>'\n                    + '<td>' + actions + '</td>'","oldText":"        function renderDevices(devices) {\n            var tb = document.getElementById('deviceTable');\n            if (!tb) return;\n            if (!devices.length) {\n                tb.innerHTML = '<tr><td colspan=\"8\" style=\"text-align:center;color:#6e7681\">暂无设备</td></tr>'; \n                return;\n            }\n            var html = devices.map(function(d) {\n                var sourceBadge = d.source === 'sadp'\n                    ? '<span class=\"badge sadp\">SADP</span>'\n                    : '<span class=\"badge manual\">手动</span>'; \n                var onlineBadge = d.online\n                    ? '<span class=\"badge online\">在线</span>'\n                    : '<span class=\"badge offline\">离线</span>'; \n                var actions = buildDeviceActions(d);\n                return '<tr>'\n                    + '<td>' + sourceBadge + '</td>' \n                    + '<td>' + (d.mac || '--') + '</td>' \n                    + '<td>' + (d.ip || '--') + '</td>' \n                    + '<td>' + (d.gateway || '--') + '</td>' \n                    + '<td>' + (d.name || d.device_name || '--') + '</td>'\n                    + '<td>' + (d.model || '--') + '</td>' \n                    + '<td>' + onlineBadge + '</td>'\n                    + '<td>' + actions + '</td>'"}],"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\index.html"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":117036,"output":1032,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":118068,"cost":{"in