{"type":"message","id":"863a65c7","parentId":"8970ff1c","timestamp":"2026-06-30T16:16:41.833Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，renderDevices()函数已经修改完成。现在需要：\n\n1. 修改refreshDevices()函数 - 让它调用新的refresh API\n2. 修改页面加载逻辑 - 先获取设备列表，异步刷新状态\n3. 删除自动刷新逻辑setInterval(refreshDevices, 15000)\n4. 修改刷新按钮 - 显示加载状态\n\n让我继续修改refreshDevices()函数。当前的refreshDevices()调用GET /api/v1/devices，现在我需要：\n- 保持原有的refreshDevices()用于获取设备列表（无状态）\n- 新增refreshDeviceStatus()用于ping检测状态\n- 页面加载时：先调用refreshDevices()获取列表，然后异步调用refreshDeviceStatus()\n- 用户点击刷新按钮：调用refreshDeviceStatus()\n\n或者更简单的方式：\n- 修改refreshDevices()为调用POST /api/v1/devices/refresh\n- 页面加载时：先快速显示列表（调用GET），然后异步调用refreshDevices()\n\n让我采用第二种方式，最小改动：\n1. 保持GET /api/v1/devices用于快速获取列表\n2. 新增refreshDeviceStatus()调用POST /api/v1/devices/refresh\n3. 页面加载时先GET，再异步POST\n4. 刷新按钮调用POST\n\n让我修改代码。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"renderDevices()修改完成。现在需要：\n\n1. 修改refreshDevices()函数 - 改为调用POST /api/v1/devices/refresh\n2. 新增快速获取设备列表的函数（页面加载时使用）\n3. 删除自动刷新逻辑\n\n让我继续修改refreshDevices()函数。按照老板的要求：\n- 页面加载：获取设备列表（无状态）→ 异步刷新状态\n- 刷新按钮：调用refresh API（ping检测）\n\n最简单的方式是修改refreshDevices()为调用refresh API，同时新增一个快速获取列表的函数用于页面加载。\n\n让我修改refreshDevices()函数："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-1aba6856ee8b40c19d0dfec2c40257a3","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"        function refreshDevices() {\n            console.log('[REFRESH] refreshDevices called');\n            var btn = document.getElementById('btnDiscover');\n            var spinner = document.getElementById('discoverSpinner');\n            if (spinner) spinner.style.display = 'inline-block';\n            return apiPost('/api/v1/devices/refresh', {}).then(function(result) {\n                console.log('[REFRESH] API response:', result);\n                if (spinner) spinner.style.display = 'none';\n                if (!result.success) {\n                    allDevices = [];\n                    renderDevices([]);\n                    return;\n                }\n                allDevices = result.data || [];\n                renderDevices(allDevices);\n                // Update dashboard counters\n                var online = allDevices.filter(function(d) { return d.status === '在线' || d.status === '已连接'; }).length;\n                var countEl = document.getElementById('devCount');\n                if (countEl) countEl.textContent = allDevices.length;\n                var onlineEl = document.getElementById('devOnline');\n                if (onlineEl) onlineEl.textContent = online;\n                var totalEl = document.getElementById('devTotal');\n                if (totalEl) totalEl.textContent = allDevices.length;\n                // Update PTZ & advanced device dropdowns\n                refreshPtzDeviceList();\n                refreshAdvancedDeviceSelectors();\n            }).catch(function(e) {\n                if (spinner) spinner.style.display = 'none';\n                console.warn('Failed to refresh devices:', e);\n            });\n        }\n        function loadDevicesQuick() {\n            // 快速获取设备列表（无状态，不ping）\n            return apiGet('/api/v1/devices').then(function(result) {\n                if (result.success) {\n                    allDevices = result.data || [];\n                    renderDevices(allDevices);\n                }\n            });\n        }","oldText":"        function refreshDevices() {\n            console.log('[REFRESH] refreshDevices called');\n            return apiGet('/api/v1/devices').then(function(result) {\n                console.log('[REFRESH] API response:', result);\n                if (!result.success) {\n                    allDevices = [];\n                    renderDevices([]);\n                    return;\n                }\n                allDevices = result.data || [];\n                renderDevices(allDevices);\n                // Update dashboard counters\n                var online = allDevices.filter(function(d) { return d.online; }).length;\n                var countEl = document.getElementById('devCount');\n                if (countEl) countEl.textContent = allDevices.length;\n                var onlineEl = document.getElementById('devOnline');\n                if (onlineEl) onlineEl.textContent = online;\n                var totalEl = document.getElementById('devTotal');\n                if (totalEl) totalEl.textContent = allDevices.length;\n                // Update PTZ & advanced device dropdowns\n                refreshPtzDeviceList();\n                refreshAdvancedDeviceSelectors();\n            }).catch(function(e) {\n                console.warn('Failed to refresh devices:', e);\n            });\n        }"}],"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\index.html"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":118103,"output":1110,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":119213,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782836165472,"responseId":"cht000d51c9@dx19f195109dd2871503"}}
