{"type":"message","id":"59bb89a3","parentId":"60382201","timestamp":"2026-06-30T16:54:34.734Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to continue the task. I just made two edits:\n1. Changed page initialization to call loadDevicesQuick() instead of refreshDevices()\n2. Changed tab switching to call loadDevicesQuick() instead of refreshDevices()\n\nNow I need to check if there are other automatic calls that need to be changed. The boss mentioned \"降低资源占用，特别是sadp发现刷新逻辑\" - reduce resource usage, especially SADP discovery refresh frequency.\n\nI've already:\n- Removed setInterval(refreshDevices, 15000) - no more 15-second auto-refresh\n- Removed autoSadpDiscover() function - no more auto SADP discovery\n- Changed page load and tab switch to use loadDevicesQuick() - no more ping on every page interaction\n\nBut I need to check if there are other places that call refreshDevices() automatically. Let me look at what other refreshDevices() calls exist.\n\nFrom the earlier search results:\n- Line 388: Changed to loadDevicesQuick()\n- Line 614: Changed to loadDevicesQuick()\n- Line 1148: Inside discoverDevices() - this is user-triggered\n- Line 1163: Function definition\n- Lines 1288, 1416, 1448, 1509, 1532: Various operations - need to check\n- Lines 2339, 2354: After IP modification\n\nI should check what lines 1288, 1416, 1448, 1509, 1532 are doing. These might be:\n- After adding a device\n- After deleting a device\n- After modifying device IP\n- After some other operation\n\nThese are likely user-triggered operations that should refresh the device list. But I need to verify they're not causing excessive resource usage.\n\nActually, the main task is \"合并自动手动设备逻辑\" - merge automatic and manual device logic. This means removing the distinction between \"manual\" and \"automatic\" (SADP) devices. I've already:\n1. Removed the source field from list_devices()\n2. Removed sourceBadge from renderDevices()\n3. Updated table headers\n\nBut I need to make sure the device list logic is correct. Let me verify the current state and check if there are any remaining issues.\n\nThe boss also said \"降低资源占用\" - reduce resource usage. The key changes I've made:\n- Removed auto-refresh (setInterval)\n- Removed auto-SADP discovery\n- Changed page load/tab switch to use loadDevicesQuick() (no ping)\n\nThis should significantly reduce resource usage. Now I need to verify the changes work correctly and there are no other issues.\n\nLet me think about what else needs to be checked:\n1. Are there any remaining references to the removed fields (source, online, etc.)?\n2. Is the device list rendering correctly without sourceBadge?\n3. Are there any other automatic calls that need to be removed?\n\nI should probably check the backend code to make sure everything is consistent. Let me also verify that the changes I made don't break anything.\n\nActually, I think the main work is done. I've:\n1. Simplified list_devices() - removed source field, simplified logic\n2. Added refresh_devices() API - uses parallel ping\n3. Updated SADP discovery - instant return\n4. Updated frontend - removed sourceBadge, added status display\n5. Removed auto-refresh mechanisms\n6. Changed page load/tab switch to use loadDevicesQuick()\n\nThe boss said to continue the task, so I should probably check if there are any remaining issues or if the changes are complete. Let me check if there are any remaining references to the old logic.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"我已经完成了两个关键修改：\n\n1. 页面初始化：改为调用 loadDevicesQuick()\n2. Tab切换：改为调用 loadDevicesQuick()\n\n这样可以避免每次页面加载或切换tab时都ping所有设备，降低资源占用。\n\n现在需要检查其他调用refreshDevices()的地方，看看是否还有自动刷新的逻辑需要处理。让我检查剩余的refreshDevices()调用：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_81c4cd6c9a464f7a895a2445","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub && Select-String -Path src\\web\\index.html -Pattern \"refreshDevices\\(\\)\" -CaseSensitive:$fals