{"type":"message","id":"91636549","parentId":"4a693b61","timestamp":"2026-06-30T17:00:03.515Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The SADP discovery endpoint is timing out. This means the SADP discovery is not working properly. Let me analyze the issue:\n\n1. The error shows it's trying to connect to port 7897 (which is the proxy port) instead of 10280 (the AstroHub port)\n2. This suggests there might be a proxy issue or the request is being routed through a proxy\n\nActually, looking at the error more carefully: `HTTPConnectionPool(host='127.0.0.1', port=7897)` - this is strange. The code is trying to connect to `http://127.0.0.1:10280/api/v1/discovery/sadp` but it's showing port 7897.\n\nThis could be because:\n1. There's a proxy configuration that's intercepting the request\n2. The request library is using a proxy\n\nLet me check if there's a proxy issue. Actually, I should test the SADP discovery directly without going through the HTTP endpoint first to see if it's a server-side issue or a client-side issue.\n\nActually, I should look at the SADP discovery code to see what's happening. The timeout=0 might be causing issues if the SADP discovery requires some time to actually discover devices.\n\nLet me think about this differently. The user wants:\n- SADP discovery to be instant (0 seconds wait)\n- But it still needs to actually discover devices\n\nThe issue might be that with timeout=0, the SADP discovery doesn't have enough time to start and discover anything. Or there's a different issue with the SADP library.\n\nLet me check the SADP discovery code to understand what's happening.\n\nActually, I should first test if the SADP discovery works at all. Let me try with a longer timeout to see if it's a timing issue.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"SADP 发现请求超时。让我检查 SADP 发现端点的实现：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_2bde0b5d747a4cddbc50653d","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":30,"offset":1,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\api\\router.py"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_21bbb78cbae94da49eafb3c5","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub && Select-String -Path src\\api\\router.py -Pattern \"discovery/sadp\" -Context 0,20"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":5275,"output":566,"cacheRead":146619,"cacheWrite":1796,"totalTokens":154256,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782838781999,"responseId":"msg_b9546f36-afff-43f2-be47-244b97246709"}}
{"type":"message","id":"6053729e","parentId":"91636549","timestamp":"2026-06-30T17:00:03.999Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_2bde0b5d747a4cddbc50653d","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\"\"\"\r\nAstroHub v2.0 - 统一路由聚合\r\n\r\n整合 M1-M11 所有模块路由到 /api/v1/ 下:\r\n- /api/v1/health            - 全局健康检查\r\n- /api/v1/discovery/sadp    - SADP 设备发现\r\n- /api/v1/devices/*         - 设备管理(真实)\r\n- /api/v1/ptz/*             - PTZ 控制(真实)\r\n- /api/v1/streams/*         - 流服务\r\n- /api/v1/calibration/*     - 校准\r\n- /api/v1/ascom/*           - ASCOM 设备\r\n- /api/v1/settings          - 系统设置\r\n\r\nAuthor: 雅痞张@南方天文\r\n\"\"\"\r\n\r\nfrom __future__ import annotations\r\n\r\nimport time\r\nfrom datetime import datetime, timezone\r\nfrom typing import Any\r\n\r\nfrom pydantic import BaseModel\r\nfrom fastapi import APIRouter, FastAPI, Query\r\nfrom fastapi.responses import JSONResponse, Response\r\n\r\n# v6.40: 操作日志\r\nfrom src.operation_logger import log_api, log_web, log_error, log_info\r\n\r\n# ================================================================ #\r\n\n[3642 more lines in file. Use offset=31 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1782838803999}}
