{"type":"message","id":"d68ab86e","parentId":"c8467ae4","timestamp":"2026-06-30T17:02:00.915Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要我继续任务。从之前的对话历史来看，主要任务是：\n1. 合并自动和手动设备逻辑\n2. 降低资源占用，特别是 SADP 发现刷新逻辑\n\n我已经完成了：\n1. 简化了 list_devices() 函数，删除了 source 字段\n2. 新增了 POST /devices/refresh API，用于并行 ping 检测设备状态\n3. 修改了 SADP 发现逻辑为即时返回\n4. 修改了前端 devices.html，删除了\"来源\"列\n5. 修改了 index.html，删除了 sourceBadge，修改了 refreshDevices() 调用新的 refresh API\n6. 删除了自动刷新 setInterval(refreshDevices, 15000)\n7. 删除了 autoSadpDiscover() 自动发现逻辑\n8. 修改了页面加载和 tab 切换使用 loadDevicesQuick() 而不是 refreshDevices()\n\n现在遇到的问题是：\n- 系统设置了代理 ProxyEnable=1, ProxyServer=127.0.0.1:7897\n- 这导致 requests 库在访问 http://127.0.0.1:10280 时，请求被路由到代理端口 7897\n- 代理没有正确转发请求，导致超时\n\n这个问题需要通过设置环境变量 NO_PROXY 或在代码中禁用代理来解决。\n\n让我先禁用代理，然后测试 SADP 发现是否正常工作。\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"发现系统设置了代理 ProxyEnable=1, ProxyServer=127.0.0.1:7897，这导致请求被路由到代理端口。让我禁用代理并测试：发现系统设置了代理导致请求被路由到代理端口。让我禁用代理并测试：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_b54138d7ab6b490d99a78750","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"$env:NO_PROXY=\"*\"; python -c \"import requests; r=requests.get('http://127.0.0.1:10280/api/v1/discovery/sadp', timeout=15); print('SADP:', r.status_code); data=r.json(); print('  count:', data.get('count', 0)); print('  devices:', [(d.get('ip'), d.get('mac')) for d in data.get('devices', [])])\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":7800,"output":498,"cacheRead":151002,"cacheWrite":611,"totalTokens":159911,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782838899292,"responseId":"msg_f1a2fd39-1a49-41f3-a360-4542f8d11c1a"}}
