{"type":"message","id":"bda8cba1","parentId":"300a4dd5","timestamp":"2026-06-30T17:03:58.427Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户说\"继续任务\"。让我看看当前情况：\n\n1. 我已经完成了大部分工作：\n   - 简化了 list_devices() 函数\n   - 新增了 POST /devices/refresh API\n   - 修改了 SADP 发现逻辑（简化为即时返回）\n   - 修改了前端删除 source badge\n   - 删除了自动刷新逻辑\n   - 修改了页面加载和tab切换使用 loadDevicesQuick()\n\n2. 现在测试结果显示：\n   - GET /devices 返回 200，有 1 台设备\n   - POST /refresh 返回 200，设备状态显示\"已连接\"\n\n3. 但是发现了一个问题：\n   - PTZDeviceController.discover_devices() 方法（ptz_controller.py:939）仍然调用 `mgr.discover_devices(timeout=3)`\n   - 这会导致每次调用 SADP 发现时都要等待 3 秒\n   - 这与老板要求的\"SADP 不需要等待，点击执行立即返回结果\"相矛盾\n\n4. 另外，我还发现：\n   - 系统代理设置导致 requests 被路由到代理端口\n   - 需要设置 NO_PROXY=\"*\" 来绕过代理\n\n5. 需要修复的问题：\n   - PTZDeviceController.discover_devices() 需要修改为即时返回\n   - 或者确保 SADP 后台服务一直在运行\n\n让我继续任务，修复 PTZDeviceController.discover_devices() 方法，使其能够即时返回已发现的设备。\n\n实际上，从之前的修改来看，我已经修改了 SADPManagerDLL.discover_devices() 方法，使其能够即时返回。但是 PTZDeviceController.discover_devices() 仍然调用它并等待 3 秒。\n\n让我检查一下这个方法的实现，看看如何修复它。\n\n另外，我还需要总结一下已完成的工作，并告诉用户任务的状态。\n\n任务总结：\n1. ✅ 简化 list_devices() - 删除 source 字段，以 MAC 为唯一标识\n2. ✅ 新增 POST /devices/refresh API - 并行 ping 检测设备状态\n3. ✅ 修改 SADP 发现逻辑 - 即时返回（但 PTZDeviceController 还在调用 timeout=3）\n4. ✅ 修改前端 - 删除 sourceBadge，删除自动刷新，修改页面加载逻辑\n5. ✅ 删除死代码 - 删除 autoSadpDiscover()、删除 setInterval\n\n还需要修复：\n- PTZDeviceController.discover_devices() 需要修改为即时返回\n\n让我继续修复这个问题。\n我已完成大部分任务。让我检查 PTZDeviceController.discover_devices() 方法，它还在调用 timeout=3：\n\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_a763ab0169e74b70886f7da5","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":50,"offset":939,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\core\\ptz_controller.py"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_3471a533d95449afbb736f61","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub && Select-String -Path src\\core\\sadp_discovery.py -Pattern \"class SADPManagerDLL\" -Context 0,5"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":6917,"output":718,"cacheRead":153684,"cacheWrite":2155,"totalTokens":163474,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782839010246,"responseId":"msg_ee8a0e94-fd6f-4280-b56c-db563b1c915a"}}
{"type":"message","id":"edd318c5","parentId":"bda8cba1","timestamp":"2026-06-30T17:03:58.906Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_a763ab0169e74b70886f7da5","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"    def discover_devices(self, bind_ip: str = \"0.0.0.0\") -> list[dict]:\r\n        \"\"\"执行 SADP 发现并返回设备列表（dict 格式）。\r\n\r\n        优先级：\r\n        1. 官方 SADP SDK (Sadp.dll ctypes)\r\n        2. 纯 Python 多播 (回退方案)\r\n        \"\"\"\r\n        # ---- 优先使用官方 SDK ----\r\n        if SADP_DLL_AVAILABLE:\r\n            LOG.log(\"info\", \"使用官方 SADP SDK 进行设备发现...\")\r\n            mgr = SADPManagerDLL()\r\n            sdk_devices = mgr.discover_devices(timeout=3)\r\n            if sdk_devices:\r\n                LOG.log(\"done\", f\"SADP SDK 发现 {len(sdk_devices)} 台设备\")\r\n                result = []\r\n                for dev_dict in sdk_devices:\r\n                    # 转换为 SADPDevice dataclass 以保持向后兼容\r\n                    dev = SADPDevice()\r\n                    dev.mac = _normalize_mac(dev_dict.get(\"mac\", \"\"))\r\n                    dev.ip = dev_dict.get(\"ip\", \"\")\r\n                    dev.subnet_mask = dev_dict.get(\"subnet_mask\", \"\")\r\n                    dev.gateway = dev_dict.get(\"gateway\", \"\")\r\n                    dev.model = dev_dict.get(\"model\", \"\")\r\n                    dev.serial_number = dev_dict.get(\"serial_number\", \"\")\r\n                    dev.device_name = dev_dict.get(\"device_name\", \"\")\r\n                    dev.firmware_version = dev_dict.get(\"firmware_version\", \"\")\r\n                    dev.activated = dev_dict.get(\"activated\", False)\r\n                    dev.is_hikvision = dev_dict.get(\"is_hikvision\", False)\r\n                    self._discovered[dev.mac] = dev\r\n                    result.append(self._sadp_to_dict(dev))\r\n                return result\r\n\r\n        # ---- 回退: 纯 Python 多播 ----\r\n        LOG.log(\"warning\", \"SADP SDK 不可用，使用纯 Python 多播发现...\")\r\n        devices = scan_for_devices(bind_ip=bind_ip)\r\n        result = []\r\n        for d in devices:\r\n            d.mac = _normalize_mac(d.mac)\r\n            self._discovered[d.mac] = d\r\n            result.append(self._sadp_to_dict(d))\r\n        return result\r\n\r\n    def get_discovered_devices(self) -> list[dict]:\r\n        \"\"\"返回已缓存的发现设备列表。\"\"\"\r\n        return [self._sadp_to_dict(d) for d in self._discovered.values()]\r\n\r\n    def _sadp_to_dict(self, d: SADPDevice) -> dict:\r\n        return {\r\n            \"mac\": d.mac,\r\n            \"ip\": d.ip,\r\n\n[1332 more lines in file. Use offset=989 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1782839038906}}
