{"type":"message","id":"a866c682","parentId":"e079ee83","timestamp":"2026-06-30T17:04:56.037Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_b29d2beba7664e9ba11520a2","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"src\\core\\ptz_controller.py:93:    [7mdef __init__[0m(self, log_dir: Path | None = None) -> None:\r\nsrc\\core\\ptz_controller.py:160:    [7mdef __init__[0m(self, local_path: Path, ptz_path: Path) -> None:\r\nsrc\\core\\ptz_controller.py:668:    [7mdef __init__[0m(self, ip: str, username: str, password: str, port: int = 80) -> None:\r\nsrc\\core\\ptz_controller.py:916:    [7mdef __init__[0m(self) -> None:"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":361,"aggregated":"src\\core\\ptz_controller.py:93:    [7mdef __init__[0m(self, log_dir: Path | None = None) -> None:\r\nsrc\\core\\ptz_controller.py:160:    [7mdef __init__[0m(self, local_path: Path, ptz_path: Path) -> None:\r\nsrc\\core\\ptz_controller.py:668:    [7mdef __init__[0m(self, ip: str, username: str, password: str, port: int = 80) -> None:\r\nsrc\\core\\ptz_controller.py:916:    [7mdef __init__[0m(self) -> None:","cwd":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1782839096037}}
{"type":"message","id":"3b4bb5f9","parentId":"a866c682","timestamp":"2026-06-30T17:04:56.039Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_e42825320a5948119cf160ef","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\r\nclass Logger:\r\n    \"\"\"全局日志器。\"\"\"\r\n    def __init__(self, log_dir: Path | None = None) -> None:\r\n        from src.config_paths import LOG_DIR as _LOG_DIR\r\n        self.log_dir = log_dir or _LOG_DIR\r\n        self.log_dir.mkdir(parents=True, exist_ok=True)\r\n        self.log_file = self._create_log_file()\r\n\r\n    def _create_log_file(self) -> Path:\r\n        today = datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y%m%d\")\r\n        existing = list(self.log_dir.glob(f\"log_{today}-*.md\"))\r\n        max_seq = 0\r\n        for f in existing:\r\n            stem = f.stem\r\n            parts = stem.rsplit(\"-\", 1)\r\n            if len(parts) == 2:\r\n                try:\r\n                    seq = int(parts[1])\r\n                    if seq > max_seq:\r\n                        max_seq = seq\r\n                except ValueError:\r\n                    continue\r\n        seq = max_seq + 1\r\n        return self.log_dir / f\"log_{today}-{seq:03d}.md\"\r\n\r\n    def log(self, level: str, message: str) -> None:\r\n        level_lower = level.lower()\r\n        if level_lower not in _ACCEPTED_LEVELS:\r\n            raise ValueError(f\"未知日志级别 '{level}'\")\r\n        timestamp = datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y%m%d-%H%M%S.%f\")[:19]\r\n        line = f\"[{level_lower}] {timestamp} - {message}\"\r\n        with open(self.log_file, \"a\", encoding=\"utf-8\") as f:\r\n            f.write(line + \"\\n\")\r\n        print(line)\r\n\r\nLOG = Logger()\r\n\r\n# ============================================================\r\n# ConfigManager\r\n# ============================================================\r\n\r\ndef _normalize_mac(mac: str) -> str:\r\n    \"\"\"统一 MAC 格式：无分隔符小写。\"\"\"\r\n    return mac.strip().replace(\":\", \"\").replace(\"-\", \"\").lower()\r\n\r\ndef _atomic_write(path: Path, data: dict) -> None:\r\n    \"\"\"通过 tempfile + os.replace() 安全写入 JSON 文件，保证原子性。\"\"\"\r\n    path = path.resolve()\r\n    dir_ = path.parent\r\n    dir_.mkdir(parents=True, exist_ok=True)\r\n    fd, tmp_path = tempfile.mkstemp(dir=dir_, suffix=\".tmp\")\r\n    try:\r\n        with os.fdopen(fd, \"w\", encoding=\"utf-8\") as f:\r\n            json.dump(data, f, indent=2, ensure_ascii=False)\r\n            f.write(\"\\n\")\r\n        os.replace(tmp_path, path)\r\n    except Exception:\r\n        try:\r\n            os.unlink(tmp_path)\r\n        except OSError:\r\n            pass\r\n        raise\r\n\r\nclass ConfigManager:\r\n    \"\"\"本地配置 + 设备配置管理器。\r\n    \r\n    v6.10: 统一使用 data/devices/{mac}/ 目录。\r\n    \"\"\"\r\n\r\n    def __init__(self, local_path: Path, ptz_path: Path) -> None:\r\n        self.local_path = local_path.resolve()\r\n        self.ptz_path = ptz_path.resolve()\r\n        from src.config_paths import DEVICES_DIR, REGISTRY_FILE\r\n        self._devices_dir = DEVICES_DIR\r\n        self._registry_file = REGISTRY_FILE\r\n        LOG.log(\"info\", f\"初始化 ConfigManager: devices_dir={self._devices_dir}\")\r\n        self.create_defaults()\r\n\r\n    def create_defaults(self) -> None:\r\n\n[2151 more lines in file. Use offset=170 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1782839096037}}
{"type":"message","id":"308ea50e","parentId":"3b4bb5f9","timestamp":"2026-06-30T17:05:11.174Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking me to continue with the task. Based on the conversation history, the main tasks are:\n\n1. Merge automatic and manual device logic - MAC as unique identifier\n2. Remove SADP waiting - instant return\n3. Remove automatic ping - manual refresh only\n4. Device IP change should show new IP (not duplicate)\n5. Clean up dead code\n\nI've already completed most of the work:\n- Modified router.py to simplify list_devices() and add refresh_devices()\n- Modified SADP discovery to instant return\n- Modified frontend to remove source badge and change refresh logic\n- Removed auto-refresh and autoSadpDiscover\n\nThe current issue is that PTZDeviceController.discover_devices() creates a new SADPManagerDLL instance every time, which means SADP is not running in the background continuously. This is why SADP discovery returns empty - the new instance starts SADP, sends inquiry, but immediately returns before devices can respond.\n\nAccording to the boss's requirements:\n- SADP should run in the background continuously\n- When user clicks \"discover\", it should return already discovered devices immediately\n- No need to wait for new discoveries\n\nSo I need to modify PTZDeviceController to:\n1. Initialize SADP in background during __init__\n2. Use a persistent SADPManagerDLL instance\n3. discover_devices() should just return cached devices from the persistent instance\n\nLet me read the __init__ method of PTZDeviceController to understand how to modify it.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_f2122a094a6144fb9948208e","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":40,"offset":916,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\core\\ptz_controller.py"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_4b4700d6f39e447fb5be9479","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":60,"offset":950,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\core\\ptz_controller.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":8515,"output":464,"cacheRead":157623,"cacheWrite":1780,"totalTokens":168382,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782839096040,"responseId":"msg_319eff5f-455f-435a-bef9-bc9f145ad2d2"}}
{"type":"message","id":"2ff6aaad","parentId":"308ea50e","timestamp":"2026-06-30T17:05:11.252Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_f2122a094a6144fb9948208e","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"    def __init__(self) -> None:\r\n        LOG.log(\"info\", \"PTZDeviceController 初始化完成\")\r\n        from src.config_paths import CONFIG_DIR as _CONFIG_DIR\r\n        self.config = ConfigManager(\r\n            local_path=_CONFIG_DIR / \"local.json\",\r\n            ptz_path=_CONFIG_DIR / \"ptz_config.json\",\r\n        )\r\n        self._clients: dict[str, ISAPIClient] = {}\r\n        self._controllers: dict[str, PTZController] = {}\r\n        # {ip: {\"username\": ..., \"password\": ..., \"port\": ...}}\r\n        self._credentials: dict[str, dict[str, str | int]] = {}\r\n        # {mac: device_info_dict} - SADP 发现缓存\r\n        self._discovered: dict[str, SADPDevice] = {}\r\n        self._credentials = {}\r\n        self._load_saved_credentials()\r\n\r\n    def get_config(self) -> ConfigManager:\r\n        return self.config\r\n\r\n    # ================================================================\r\n    #  SADP 发现 & 设备管理\r\n    # ================================================================\r\n\r\n    def discover_devices(self, bind_ip: str = \"0.0.0.0\") -> list[dict]:\r\n        \"\"\"执行 SADP 发现并返回设备列表（dict 格式）。\r\n\r\n        优先级：\r\n        1. 官方 SADP SDK (Sadp.dll ctypes)\r\n        2. 纯 Python 多播 (回退方案)\r\n        \"\"\"\r\n        # ---- 优先使用官方 SDK ----\r\n        if SADP_DLL_AVAILABLE:\r\n            LOG.log(\"info\", \"使用官方 SADP SDK 进行设备发现...\")\r\n            mgr = SADPManagerDLL()\r\n            sdk_devices = mgr.discover_devices(timeout=3)\r\n            if sdk_devices:\r\n                LOG.log(\"done\", f\"SADP SDK 发现 {len(sdk_devices)} 台设备\")\r\n                result = []\r\n                for dev_dict in sdk_devices:\r\n                    # 转换为 SADPDevice dataclass 以保持向后兼容\r\n\n[1365 more lines in file. Use offset=956 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1782839111252}}
{"type":"message","id":"f67c248a","parentId":"2ff6aaad","timestamp":"2026-06-30T17:05:11.252Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_4b4700d6f39e447fb5be9479","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"            sdk_devices = mgr.discover_devices(timeout=3)\r\n            if sdk_devices:\r\n                LOG.log(\"done\", f\"SADP SDK 发现 {len(sdk_devices)} 台设备\")\r\n                result = []\r\n                for dev_dict in sdk_devices:\r\n                    # 转换为 SADPDevice dataclass 以保持向后兼容\r\n                    dev = SADPDevice()\r\n                    dev.mac = _normalize_mac(dev_dict.get(\"mac\", \"\"))\r\n                    dev.ip = dev_dict.get(\"ip\", \"\")\r\n                    dev.subnet_mask = dev_dict.get(\"subnet_mask\", \"\")\r\n                    dev.gateway = dev_dict.get(\"gateway\", \"\")\r\n                    dev.model = dev_dict.get(\"model\", \"\")\r\n                    dev.serial_number = dev_dict.get(\"serial_number\", \"\")\r\n                    dev.device_name = dev_dict.get(\"device_name\", \"\")\r\n                    dev.firmware_version = dev_dict.get(\"firmware_version\", \"\")\r\n                    dev.activated = dev_dict.get(\"activated\", False)\r\n                    dev.is_hikvision = dev_dict.get(\"is_hikvision\", False)\r\n                    self._discovered[dev.mac] = dev\r\n                    result.append(self._sadp_to_dict(dev))\r\n                return result\r\n\r\n        # ---- 回退: 纯 Python 多播 ----\r\n        LOG.log(\"warning\", \"SADP SDK 不可用，使用纯 Python 多播发现...\")\r\n        devices = scan_for_devices(bind_ip=bind_ip)\r\n        result = []\r\n        for d in devices:\r\n            d.mac = _normalize_mac(d.mac)\r\n            self._discovered[d.mac] = d\r\n            result.append(self._sadp_to_dict(d))\r\n        return result\r\n\r\n    def get_discovered_devices(self) -> list[dict]:\r\n        \"\"\"返回已缓存的发现设备列表。\"\"\"\r\n        return [self._sadp_to_dict(d) for d in self._discovered.values()]\r\n\r\n    def _sadp_to_dict(self, d: SADPDevice) -> dict:\r\n        return {\r\n            \"mac\": d.mac,\r\n            \"ip\": d.ip,\r\n            \"subnet_mask\": d.subnet_mask,\r\n            \"gateway\": d.gateway,\r\n            \"model\": d.model,\r\n            \"serial_number\": d.serial_number,\r\n            \"device_name\": d.device_name,\r\n            \"firmware_version\": d.firmware_version,\r\n            \"activated\": d.activated,\r\n            \"is_hikvision\": d.is_hikvision,\r\n            \"source\": \"sadp\",\r\n        }\r\n\r\n    # ================================================================\r\n    #  凭据管理\r\n    # ================================================================\r\n\r\n    def save_credentials(self, ip: str, username: str, password: str,\r\n                         port: int = 80, mac: str = \"\", model: str = \"\",\r\n                         name: str = \"\") -> None:\r\n        \"\"\"保存设备凭据到内存 + 配置文件。\r\n        \r\n        v7.17: 必须有真实 MAC 地址才能保存。\r\n\n[1311 more lines in file. Use offset=1010 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1782839111252}}
