：\n\n**当前问题**：\n- `PTZDeviceController.discover_devices()` 每次创建新的 `SADPManagerDLL()` 实例\n- 新实例启动SADP后立即返回，设备没有时间响应\n- 导致SADP发现返回空列表\n\n**修改方案**：\n1. 在 `PTZDeviceController.__init__()` 中初始化持久化的 `SADPManagerDLL` 实例\n2. 修改 `discover_devices()` 使用持久化实例，timeout=0 即时返回\n3. 让SADP在后台持续运行\n\n让我修改代码：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_b24f4e33107d4f2d879cec8b","name":"edit","arguments":{}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":63511,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":63511,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"aborted","timestamp":1782839111257,"responseId":"msg_01ed7f2f-aa50-4a25-90af-ce84ddf3c02b","errorMessage":"This operation was aborted"}}
