{"type":"message","id":"dedeffb6","parentId":"d9ea4224","timestamp":"2026-06-30T17:10:57.003Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The system is asking me to store durable memories to memory/2026-07-01.md before the session ends. I need to capture the key work done in this session:\n\n1. Fixed SADP discovery 500 error (added SDK/hik/ search path)\n2. Fixed device gateway display for SADP-only devices\n3. Fixed speed test ZOOM grouping display\n4. Major refactoring of device management - removing manual/auto source distinction\n5. Simplified device list API with MAC as unique identifier\n6. Added refresh API for online status detection\n7. Modified SADP discovery to be instant (0 seconds)\n8. Removed automatic refresh logic\n\nThis was a productive session with significant architectural changes. I should document the key decisions and outcomes.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_9e22c7bbb489495bbffdd0ac","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# 2026-07-01 工作记录\n\n## 设备管理架构重构（进行中）\n\n### 核心决策\n**MAC = 设备唯一标识**，删除\"手动/自动\"来源区分。\n\n### 已完成的修改\n\n#### 1. SADP 发现 500 错误修复\n- **根因**：`_find_sadp_dll()` 搜索路径 `SDK/Sadp.dll`，实际文件在 `SDK/hik/Sadp.dll`\n- **修复**：在 `sadp_discovery.py` 第268行增加 `SDK_LIBS_DIR / \"hik\" / \"Sadp.dll\"` 优先路径\n\n#### 2. 设备网关显示修复\n- **问题**：纯 SADP 发现设备缺少 gateway 字段\n- **修复**：`router.py` 第445行，SADP-only 设备字典补上 `gateway` 和 `subnet_mask`\n\n#### 3. 速度测试 ZOOM 分组显示\n- **问题**：后端返回 `by_zoom` 字段，前端未使用\n- **修复**：`advanced.html` 第411行后，添加 ZOOM 分组表格（+19行）\n\n#### 4. 设备列表 API 简化\n- **删除**：Pass 1/Pass 2 合并逻辑、`source` 字段\n- **新逻辑**：以 MAC 为唯一键，存储设备为基础，SADP 发现更新 IP/型号/网关\n- **时间**：0秒（即时返回）\n\n#### 5. 新增刷新 API\n- **端点**：`POST /api/v1/devices/refresh`\n- **功能**：并行 ping 所有设备（ThreadPoolExecutor），timeout=1s\n- **状态**：在线 | 离线 | 已连接（基于连接池）\n- **时间**：1-2秒（并行）\n\n#### 6. SADP 发现改为即时返回\n- **删除**：`timeout` 等待循环、`SendInquiry` 后等待\n- **新逻辑**：SADP 后台持续运行，直接返回已发现设备\n- **时间**：0秒\n\n#### 7. 前端修改\n- **删除**：sourceBadge 渲染、`setInterval(refreshDevices, 15000)` 自动刷新\n- **新增**：`loadDevicesQuick()` 快速加载、`refreshDevices()` 调用 POST refresh API\n- **按钮**：点击刷新 → POST /api/v1/devices/refresh\n\n### 待完成\n- [ ] 测试 SADP 后台持续运行是否稳定\n- [ ] 验证 MAC 去重逻辑无冲突\n- [ ] 死代码清理检查\n\n### 备份\n- `backup_20260701_000240/` - 重构前完整备份\n\n### 关键技术点\n- **并行 ping**：ThreadPoolExecutor，每个 timeout=1s，总时间 1-2秒\n- **设备状态**：基于 IP 可达性 + 连接池状态\n- **SADP 架构**：后台持续运行，发现设备缓存，即时返回\n\n### 老板反馈\n- \"一个设备不可能有2个IP且都可达\" - 强调 MAC 唯一性\n- \"禁止过度开发\" - 最小改动原则\n- \"降低资源占用\" - 移除自动刷新，改为手动触发\n","path":"memory/2026-07-01.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":4610,"output":966,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":66452,"totalTokens":72028,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782839433897,"responseId":"msg_9f8a51d2-fe16-4c24-8959-0fec724de1f5"}}
