 to the SADP module and not exposed to the API.\n\nLooking at the code flow:\n1. router.py `list_devices()` calls `mgr.list_stored_devices()` and `mgr.get_discovered_devices()`\n2. `list_stored_devices()` in ptz_controller.py was updated to not include source field ✅\n3. `get_discovered_devices()` calls `_sadp_to_dict()` which was also updated ✅\n\nBut the SADP module itself (`sadp_discovery.py`) has a `_device_to_dict()` method that still includes \"source\": \"sadp\". This might be used internally and then the result is passed through `_sadp_to_dict()` in ptz_controller.py which strips the source field.\n\nHowever, to be consistent and clean, we should remove this field from sadp_discovery.py as well.\n\nBut wait, the user asked me to \"continue the task\" (继续任务), which means I should complete the remaining work. The verification shows the API is working correctly, but there's still a \"source\" field in sadp_discovery.py that should be cleaned up for consistency.\n\nLet me check what this field is for and if it needs to be removed.\n发现 `sadp_discovery.py:1276` 还有 `\"source\": \"sadp\"` 字段。让我检查并清理：\n\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"用户说\"继续任务\"。我检查了之前的验证结果：\n\n**已完成的工作**：\n1. ✅ 简化设备列表 API，删除 source 字段\n2. ✅ 删除自动 SADP 发现逻辑\n3. ✅ 删除自动刷新（setInterval）\n4. ✅ 新增手动刷新 API（POST /devices/refresh）\n5. ✅ SADP 发现改为即时返回（0秒）\n6. ✅ 前端删除 sourceBadge 渲染\n7. ✅ 修改 isAdded 逻辑，使用 has_credentials 替代 source\n8. ✅ 清理 ptz_controller.py 和 router.py 中的死代码\n\n**验证结果**：\n- GET /api/v1/devices: 200 ✅，无 source 字段 ✅\n- POST /api/v1/devices/refresh: 200 ✅，0.04秒 ✅，有 status 字段 ✅\n- GET /api/v1/discovery/sadp: 200 ✅，0.0秒 ✅\n\n**发现的问题**：\n- `sadp_discovery.py:1276` 还有 `\"source\": \"sadp\"` 字段\n\n现在我需要检查这个字段是否需要删除。让我查看这部分代码。\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_80d08c4f856e4ed8b6cd29fb","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":30,"offset":1260,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\core\\sadp_discovery.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","mode