ition at line 542. This is an internal data structure. Let me check if it's actually used anywhere.\n\nLooking at the code:\n- The dataclass has a `source` field with default \"sadp\"\n- But _device_to_dict doesn't include it in the output\n- The frontend doesn't use it\n\nSo this field is essentially dead code - it's defined but never used in any output. I should remove it to complete the cleanup.\n\n8. Let me verify the complete task status:\n   - ✅ SADP discovery is instant (0.01s)\n   - ✅ No \"source\" field in API responses\n   - ✅ No \"来源\" column in frontend table\n   - ✅ No \"sourceBadge\" in frontend rendering\n   - ✅ Manual refresh button works (POST /refresh)\n   - ✅ No auto-refresh interval\n   - ✅ No autoSadpDiscover() function\n   - ✅ loadDevicesQuick() for instant load\n   - ✅ MAC-based device identification\n   - ⚠️ SADPDevice dataclass still has unused `source` field\n\n9. The remaining cleanup is to remove the unused `source` field from the SADPDevice dataclass. This completes the \"dead code removal\" requirement.\n\n10. I should provide a final summary to the boss showing the complete task is done.\nThe SADPDevice dataclass still has `source: str = \"sadp\"` field - this is internal, but let me check if it's actually used anywhere, since it's not in any output. If it's dead code, should remove it:\n\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_4c87a02c466e4b62b586b07b","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub && Select-String -Path src\\core\\sadp_discovery.py -Pattern \"\\.source|source=\" -CaseSensitive:$false | Select-Object -First 20"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_1d9add25b2fa4e148021a860","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub && Select-String -Path src\\core\\ptz_controller.py -Pattern \"\\.source|source=\" -CaseSensitive:$false | Select-Object -First 10"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_6095eeb16e89445c8b5