{"type":"message","id":"0ed4b1b9","parentId":"bb253dfc","timestamp":"2026-06-30T17:41:34.741Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"截图已生成，但我需要导航到设备页面再截图。当前截图是仪表盘页面。让我导航到设备页面。\n\n另外，之前的截图可能不是设备页面，需要切换到设备管理页面。让我用 Selenium 导航到设备页面。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"截图已生成，但需要导航到设备管理页面。\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_66b483e182724d168975632a","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub; python -c \"\nfrom selenium import webdriver\nfrom selenium.webdriver.chrome.options import Options\nfrom selenium.webdriver.common.by import By\nimport time\n\nopt = Options()\nopt.add_argument('--headless')\nopt.add_argument('--window-size=1920,1080')\nopt.add_argument('--no-sandbox')\ndriver = webdriver.Chrome(options=opt)\n\n# 导航到设备页面\ndriver.get('http://127.0.0.1:10280/#devices')\ntime.sleep(3)\n\n# 点击设备导航按钮\ntry:\n    nav_btns = driver.find_elements(By.CSS_SELECTOR, '.nav-btn')\n    for btn in nav_btns:\n        if '设备' in btn.text or 'devices' in btn.get_attribute('data-page'):\n            btn.click()\n            time.sleep(2)\n            break\nexcept Exception as e:\n    print('导航异常:', e)\n\n# 保存截图\ndriver.save_screenshot('test_device_list.png')\nprint('截图已保存: test_device_list.png')\ndriver.quit()\n\"","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":4405,"output":359,"cacheRead":209008,"cacheWrite":4512,"totalTokens":218284,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782841280644,"responseId":"msg_faf8866f-3861-478d-bf97-3a089bb3ca2b"}}
