{"type":"message","id":"b31dc196","parentId":"467019bc","timestamp":"2026-06-30T17:42:34.380Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user said \"继续\" (continue). I was in the middle of an end-to-end test. The image analysis tool failed with \"Unknown model: ali/qwen3.7-plus\". This is a configuration issue with the image model.\n\nLet me analyze the situation:\n1. I took a screenshot of the device list page\n2. The image analysis tool failed due to model configuration\n3. I need to find an alternative way to verify the changes\n\nOptions:\n1. Try to use the vision.py script that's mentioned in TOOLS.md\n2. Read the screenshot directly if the system supports it\n3. Use a different approach - maybe just verify via API responses\n\nLooking at TOOLS.md, there's a vision.py script mentioned:\n```bash\n# 单图分析\npython astrohub/tools/vision.py <图片路径> \"分析提示词\"\n```\n\nLet me try that approach.\n\nActually, wait - the user is asking me to continue. Let me check what the current state is. The screenshot was taken successfully. The image analysis failed. I should either:\n1. Use the vision.py script\n2. Or just verify via the existing API responses that I already have\n\nLooking at the conversation flow, I've already verified:\n- API returns 200 with correct fields (no 'source' field)\n- SADP discovery returns in 0.01s\n- Refresh returns in 0.04s with status field\n\nThe main remaining verification is to confirm the frontend doesn't show the \"来源\" column. Since the image tool is broken, let me use the vision.py script mentioned in TOOLS.md.\n\nWait, the path in TOOLS.md is `astrohub/tools/vision.py` but I'm already in the astrohub directory. Let me check the correct path.\n\nFrom TOOLS.md:\n```\n### 便捷脚本\n\n```bash\n# 单图分析\npython astrohub/tools/vision.py <图片路径> \"分析提示词\"\n\n# 多图分析（拼接多个 base64）\npython astrohub/tools/vision.py screenshot.png \"描述这个截图中的UI和状态\"\n```\n\n脚本位置：`astrohub/tools/vision.py`\n```\n\nSo the script is at `astrohub/tools/vision.py` relative to the parent directory, which would be `C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\tools\\vision.py` from the astrohub directory.\n\nLet me try running it.\n`image` 工具配置异常，改用 `vision.py` 脚本分析截图。\n\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_22f9c5c54f2744e389d1a3ea","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub && python tools/vision.py test_device_list.png \"详细分析这个设备管理页面截图：1) 列出表格所有列名（按顺序）；2) 确认是否有'来源'列或'手动/自动'标签；3) 列出设备数据（MAC、IP、网关等）；4) 列出所有按钮名称。\"","timeout":60}},{"type":"text","text":"\n</think>\n\n图片分析工具报错了，模型配置有问题。让我用其他方式验证 - 我可以用 Python 直接调用 API 来验证，或者用其他方法分析截图。\n\n让我先检查图片是否有效，然后用其他方式验证。图片分析工具失败了。让我用其他方式验证 - 直接通过 API 测试和检查 HTML 源码：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_9125c49c4a0043609c1adc1b","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub; python -c \"\nfrom PIL import Image\nimg = Image.open('test_device_list.png')\nprint(f'图片尺寸: {img.size}')\nprint(f'图片模式: {img.mode}')\nprint('图片加载成功')\n\""}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_badcb8b7076a4236b019af5c","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub; python -c \"\nimport requests\n# 测试设备列表API - 验证无source字段\nr = requests.get('http://127.0.0.1:10280/api/v1/devices', timeout=5, proxies={'http':None,'https':None})\ndata = r.json()\nif data.get('data'):\n    dev = data['data'][0]\n    print('=== 设备数据字段验证 ===')\n    print(f'字段列表: {list(dev.keys())}')\n    print(f'source字段存在: {\\\"source\\\" in dev}')\n    print(f'has_credentials字段存在: {\\\"has_credentials\\\" in dev}')\n    print()\n    print('=== 设备详情 ===')\n    for k,v in dev.items():\n        print(f'  {k}: {v}')\n\""}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_b883f76fc4324818993252d0","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub; Select-String -Path src\\web\\includes\\devices.html -Pattern \"<th>来源</th>|<th>source</th>\" -CaseSensitive:$false"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_1b0cea37b9af4a5081250ef7","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub; Select-String -Path src\\web\\index.html -Pattern \"sourceBadge|d\\.source\\s*===\" -CaseSensitive:$false"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_6f9a8836fe3f4eb9ba876817","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub; python -c \"\nimport requests\n# 测试刷新API\nr = requests.post('http://127.0.0.1:10280/api/v1/devices/refresh', timeout=10, proxies={'http':None,'https':None})\ndata = r.json()\nif data.get('data'):\n    dev = data['data'][0]\n    print('=== 刷新API字段验证 ===')\n    print(f'字段列表: {list(dev.keys())}')\n    print(f'source字段存在: {\\\"source\\\" in dev}')\n    print(f'status字段: {dev.get(\\\"status\\\")}')\n\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":1874,"output":1401,"cacheRead":216503,"cacheWrite":390,"totalTokens":220168,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782841319260,"responseId":"msg_79ddc479-cac8-4e08-beed-05f68989fb89"}}
