{"type":"message","id":"3f7cc6bd","parentId":"d3a9a4b7","timestamp":"2026-06-30T17:43:43.746Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The screenshot shows the device management page. Let me analyze it:\n\n1. **Table columns** (from left to right): MAC, IP, 网关, 名称, 型号, 状态, 操作\n2. **No \"来源\" (source) column** ✅\n3. **No sourceBadge** - the device shows \"在线\" status badge ✅\n4. **Buttons**: 发现设备, 添加设备, 刷新 ✅\n5. **Device data**: MAC=240f9b764193, IP=192.168.5.72, 网关=192.168.5.1, 名称=4k 32X DC, 型号=iDS-2DF8C832IXS-A, 状态=在线(红色badge)\n6. **Actions**: toggle switch, 信息 button, 删除 button\n7. **Localhost info** shows correctly: Astro-AIO, AMD Ryzen 7 5700G, 64GB, RTX 5060 Ti, 192.168.5.201, 192.168.5.1\n\nAPI verification:\n- GET /devices: fields = ['mac', 'ip', 'name', 'model', 'gateway', 'subnet_mask', 'has_credentials'], source: False ✅\n- POST /refresh: fields = ['mac', 'ip', 'name', 'model', 'gateway', 'subnet_mask', 'has_credentials', 'status'], source: False, status: 已连接 ✅\n- No \"来源\" th in devices.html ✅\n- No \"sourceBadge\" or \"d.source\" in index.html ✅\n\nNote: There's still `.badge.manual` CSS class in index.html (line 93) but it's unused - it's just CSS that's not referenced anymore. This is minor dead CSS, not functional dead code.\n\nEverything looks good. The task is complete. Let me summarize the E2E test results.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"截图已获取，端到端测试验证完成 ✅\n\n## 端到端测试报告\n\n### 截图验证（视觉确认）\n\n| 验证项 | 结果 |\n|--------|------|\n| 表格列：MAC, IP, 网关, 名称, 型号, 状态, 操作 | ✅ 正确 |\n| **\"来源\"列不存在** | ✅ 已删除 |\n| 设备数据完整显示 | ✅ |\n| 状态列显示\"在线\"badge | ✅ |\n| 按钮：发现设备 / 添加设备 / 刷新 | ✅ 正确 |\n| 无\"手动/自动\"标签 | ✅ 已删除 |\n\n### API 验证\n\n```\nGET /devices:\n  字段: mac, ip, name, model, gateway, subnet_mask, has_credentials\n  source: False ✅\n\nPOST /devices/refresh:\n  字段: mac, ip, name, model, gateway, subnet_mask, has_credentials, status\n  source: False ✅\n  status: 已连接 ✅\n```\n\n### 前端代码验证\n\n```\ndevices.html \"来源\"列:   无 ✅\nindex.html sourceBadge:  无 ✅\nindex.html d.source:     无 ✅\n```\n\n### 残留（无影响）\n\n- `index.html:93` 有 `.badge.manual` CSS 样式定义 — 未使用，不影响功能\n\n---\n\n**结论：所有修复已生效，设备管理逻辑重构完成 ✅**"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":6,"output":762,"cacheRead":17379,"cacheWrite":206209,"totalTokens":224356,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782841389885,"responseId":"msg_321315fd-c772-4367-9e05-e7f1b9729c69"}}
