{"type":"message","id":"098478ec","parentId":"0c222385","timestamp":"2026-06-30T17:45:47.978Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user asked me to continue the E2E test. Let me look at what happened:\n\n1. I took a screenshot of the device management page\n2. The screenshot was captured successfully (68KB, 1904x929 pixels)\n3. The `image` tool failed with \"Unknown model: ali/qwen-3.7-max\"\n4. The `vision.py` script doesn't exist\n5. I ran several verification commands\n\nFrom the results I can see:\n- `test_device_list.png` exists and is valid (RGB, 1904x929)\n- API fields don't contain 'source': `['mac', 'ip', 'name', 'model', 'gateway', 'subnet_mask', 'has_credentials']`\n- Refresh API fields: `['mac', 'ip', 'name', 'model', 'gateway', 'subnet_mask', 'has_credentials', 'status']`\n- No \"来源\" column in devices.html\n- No \"sourceBadge\" or \"d.source ===\" in index.html\n- There's a `.badge.manual` CSS class in index.html:93 - this is a CSS class definition that's no longer used\n\nI need to:\n1. Remove the unused `.badge.manual` CSS class (dead code cleanup)\n2. Remove the `.badge.sadp` CSS class too if it exists\n3. Complete the visual analysis of the screenshot\n4. Summarize the E2E test results\n\nLet me check the CSS and remove dead badge styles, then do a proper image analysis.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"发现残留死代码：CSS 中的 `.badge.manual` 样式（index.html:93）已无用。清理并继续：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_b55de0ad03094accbb686c7e","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub; Select-String -Path src\\web\\index.html -Pattern \"badge\\.sadp|badge\\.manual|badge\\.online|badge\\.offline\" -CaseSensitive:$false"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_9bc30ed9a176460b96bd2607","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":30,"offset":88,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\index.html"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP