{"type":"compaction","id":"a1f0b291","parentId":"0bc11289","timestamp":"2026-06-30T20:24:41.647Z","summary":"## Goal\nRefactor AstroHub device management to merge automatic (SADP) and manual device logic, using MAC as the unique identifier. Eliminate \"source\" field distinctions, implement instant SADP discovery, enable manual status refresh via parallel ping, and clean up all related dead code.\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- **Precision**: Exact modifications only; no over-engineering.\n- **Performance**: SADP discovery must return instantly (0s); Refresh API must be fast (~0.04s).\n- **Logic**: One device = one record (MAC-based). IP changes update the existing record.\n- **Cleanup**: Remove all dead code, including unused fields, functions, and comments.\n- **Backup**: Always backup before iteration (`backup_20260701_000240/`).\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- [x] **Backend `router.py`**: Simplified `list_devices()` (removed source/merge logic); Added `POST /devices/refresh` for parallel ping status detection.\n- [x] **Backend `ptz_controller.py`**: Initialized persistent `SADPManagerDLL` in `__init__`; Modified `discover_devices()` to use persistent instance for instant return; Removed `source` fields from `_sadp_to_dict` and `list_stored_devices`.\n- [x] **Backend `sadp_discovery.py`**: Fixed DLL path (`SDK/hik/Sadp.dll`); Modified `discover_devices()` for instant return; Removed `source` field from `_device_to_dict` and `SADPDevice` dataclass.\n- [x] **Frontend `index.html`**: Removed `sourceBadge` rendering; Deleted `setInterval` auto-refresh and `autoSadpDiscover()`; Added `loadDevicesQuick()`; Updated `refreshDevices()` to call POST API; Updated `isAdded` logic to use `has_credentials`; Cleaned up v7.117 comments.\n- [x] **Frontend `devices.html`**: Removed \"Source\" column from table header.\n- [x] **Verification**: All APIs return 200 with correct fields (no `source`). SADP returns in 0.01s; Refresh returns in 0.04s. No dead code residues found.\n\n### In Progress\n- [ ] None (Task complete, awaiting acceptance).\n\n### Blocked\n- [ ] None.\n\n## Key Decisions\n- **MAC Uniqueness**: Device identity is strictly based on MAC address. Manual and SADP records are merged by MAC, not IP or source type.\n- **Persistent SADP**: SADP service starts at controller initialization and runs in the background, allowing instant discovery without waiting for multicast timeouts.\n- **Manual Refresh**: Automatic polling is removed. Status updates occur only when the user clicks \"Refresh\", triggering a parallel ping of all devices.\n\n## Next Steps\n1. Wait for user acceptance of the refactored device man\n\n[Compaction summary truncated to fit budget]\n\n**Turn Context (split turn):**\n\n## Goal\n清理 `astrohub` 目录中的临时文件，包括过程编辑脚本、缓存文件、截图、录像等。\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- (none)\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- [x] 执行 PowerShell 命令列出匹配的文件和目录。\n\n### In Progress\n- [ ] 删除识别出的临时文件和目录。\n\n### Blocked\n- 最后的工具调用返回了退出代码 1（可能因命令截断或语法错误导致），但之前的列表命令已成功执行并返回了结果。\n\n## Key Decisions\n- **识别规则**：使用正则表达式匹配文件名/目录名，包括 `test_`, `.pyc`, `backup_`, `.cache`, `.tmp`, `.screenshot`, `.png`, `.jpg`, `.mp4`, `.avi` 以及目录 `__pycache__`, `temp` 等。\n\n## Next Steps\n1. 根据已列出的文件列表，执行删除操作。\n2. 确认删除成功。\n\n## Critical Context\n- 目标路径: `C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub`\n- 需要清理的文件类型示例:\n    - 截图: `test_device_list.png`, `step1_dashboard.png` 等位于 `astrohub\\screenshots_v7.103\\` 和 `astrohub\\tools\\screenshots\\`。\n    - 备份目录: `backup_20260616_105423`, `backup_20260618`, `backup_20260620` 等多个以 `backup_` 开头的目录。\n    - 缓存: `.pytest_cache`。\n    - 数据文件: `data\\downloads\\image\\` 和 `data\\records\\` 下的 `.jpg`, `.mp4` 文件。\n\n## Decisions\n- 采用 PowerShell 的 `Get-ChildItem` 配合 `Where-Object` 进行递归搜索和过滤。\n\n## Open TODOs\n- 执行删除命令清理已识别的文件和目录。\n\n## Constraints/Rules\n- 仅清理临时文件、缓存、截图、录像和备份，不删除核心代码或配置文件（除非它们匹配上述模式，需谨慎）。\n\n## Pending user asks\n- (none) - 用户请求已在进行中。\n\n## Exact identifiers\n- Chat ID: `telegram:8447197723`\n- Message ID: `44288`\n-