{"type":"message","id":"dca2555f","parentId":"aa726d00","timestamp":"2026-06-30T20:26:36.711Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me analyze the three issues the user raised and create a fix plan for review.\n\n1. Disconnect/connect device - no success/failure notifications showing\n2. Device management page shows offline even when connected - need async refresh on page load\n3. Reorder columns in device management table\n\nLet me first read the relevant files to understand current behavior.让我先检查相关代码，整理修复计划。\n\nI can see:\n1. The table columns are currently: MAC, IP, 网关, 名称, 型号, 状态, 操作\n2. User wants: 序号, 设备型号, 设备名称, MAC, IP地址, 网关地址, 状态, 操作\n\n\n3. I need to examine the JavaScript files to understand how the connection and disconnection handlers work, and trace through the page initialization logic to see why the device status isn't updating correctly on load.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_d49b6d998e20459293514f30","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub; Select-String -Path \"src\\web\\index.html\" -Pattern \"function connectDevice|function disconnectDevice|function loadDevices|function refreshDevices|function switchPage|page-devices\" | Select-Object LineNumber, Line | Format-Table -AutoSize"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":6,"output":286,"cacheRead":31858,"cacheWrite":2829,"totalTokens":34979,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782851189294,"responseId":"msg_f9784eb5-de43-4446-8777-62ca3fee2552"}}
{"type":"message","id":"b94d2d0b","parentId":"dca2555f","timestamp":"2026-06-30T20:26:37.208Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_d49b6d998e20459293514f30","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[32;1mLineNumber[0m[32;1m Line[0m\r\n[32;1m----------[0m [32;1m----[0m\r\n      1160         function refreshDevices() {\r\n      1191         function loadDevicesQuick() {\r\n      1322         function connectDevice(ip) {\r\n      1438         function connectDeviceWithCreds(ip, username, password, port) {\r\n      1477         function disconnectDevice(ip) {"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":369,"aggregated":"[32;1mLineNumber[0m[32;1m Line[0m\r\n[32;1m----------[0m [32;1m----[0m\r\n      1160         function refreshDevices() {\r\n      1191         function loadDevicesQuick() {\r\n      1322         function connectDevice(ip) {\r\n      1438         function connectDeviceWithCreds(ip, username, password, port) {\r\n      1477         function disconnectDevice(ip) {","cwd":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1782851197208}}
{"type":"message","id":"545bb43d","parentId":"b94d2d0b","timestamp":"2026-06-30T20:26:45.629Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me look at the connectDevice, disconnectDevice functions, and the switchPage/navigation logic.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_2ad30872ca194329abf27dde","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":50,"offset":1322,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\index.html"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_ba80841c5d1648fda27510b5","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":30,"offset":1477,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\index.html"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_5a1cbd5dbbd4457fb06e9f37","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub; Select-String -Path \"src\\web\\index.html\" -Pattern \"switchPage|loadDevicesQuick|refreshDevices\" | Select-Object LineNumber, Line | Format-Table -AutoSize"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":6,"output":254,"cacheRead":31858,"cacheWrite":3244,"totalTokens":35362,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782851197209,"responseId":"msg_3a25fc96-7dd0-47af-a746-5803a848021c"}}
{"type":"message","id":"52d6bd3d","parentId":"545bb43d","timestamp":"2026-06-30T20:26:46.118Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_2ad30872ca194329abf27dde","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"        function connectDevice(ip) {\r\n            // v6.54: 防止重复点击\r\n            if (_connectionOperationInProgress) {\r\n                showToast('warning', '请等待上一次操作完成');\r\n                return;\r\n            }\r\n            _connectionOperationInProgress = true;\r\n\r\n            addLog('info', '正在连接设备: ' + ip);\r\n            showToast('info', '正在连接设备...');\r\n\r\n            // 禁用连接按钮\r\n            if (window.setConnectionButtonsEnabled) window.setConnectionButtonsEnabled(false);\r\n\r\n            // 先获取 credentials\r\n            apiGet('/api/v1/ptz/devices/' + ip + '/credentials').then(function(creds) {\r\n                var username = (creds && creds.success) ? creds.username : 'admin';\r\n                var password = (creds && creds.success) ? creds.password : '';\r\n                var port = (creds && creds.success) ? (creds.port || 80) : 80;\r\n\r\n                // 再调用 connect API\r\n                apiPost('/api/v1/devices/' + ip + '/connect', { username: username, password: password, port: port }).then(function(result) {\r\n                    if (result && result.success) {\r\n                        addLog('success', result.message || '连接成功');\r\n                        // Set connectedDevice BEFORE refreshDevices\r\n                        var dev = allDevices.find(function(d) { return d.ip === ip; }) || { ip: ip };\r\n                        window.connectedDevice = {\r\n                            ip: dev.ip, model: dev.model || '', name: dev.name || '', device_name: dev.device_name || '',\r\n                            mac: dev.mac || '', username: username, password: password, port: port, online: true\r\n                        };\r\n                        // Update button immediately\r\n                        if (window.updateDeviceStatus) window.updateDeviceStatus();\r\n                        // v7.31: 连接成功后立即启用所有控件\r\n                        if (window.enableAllControls) window.enableAllControls();\r\n                        // WASM SDK: 同步登录设备\r\n                        if (typeof onDeviceConnected === 'function') onDeviceConnected();\r\n                        // 动态加载设备图像参数(白平衡、快门、光圈、降噪、锐度、OSD)\r\n                        // v5.42: 增加延迟确保设备连接完成\r\n                        setTimeout(function() {\r\n                            console.log('[CONNECT] Calling loadDeviceImageParams for:', ip);\r\n                            if (typeof loadDeviceImageParams === 'function') {\r\n                                loadDeviceImageParams(ip);\r\n                                console.log('[CONNECT] loadDeviceImageParams called');\r\n                            } else {\r\n                                console.error('[CONNECT] loadDeviceImageParams not found');\r\n                            }\r\n                            // 加载对焦模式\r\n                            if (typeof loadFocusMode === 'function') {\r\n                                loadFocusMode();\r\n                            }\r\n\n[1498 more lines in file. Use offset=1372 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1782851206118}}
{"type":"message","id":"ba6625ee","parentId":"52d6bd3d","timestamp":"2026-06-30T20:26:46.118Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_ba80841c5d1648fda27510b5","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"        function disconnectDevice(ip) {\r\n            // v6.54: 防止重复点击\r\n            if (_connectionOperationInProgress) {\r\n                showToast('warning', '请等待上一次操作完成');\r\n                return;\r\n            }\r\n            _connectionOperationInProgress = true;\r\n\r\n            // 禁用连接按钮\r\n            if (window.setConnectionButtonsEnabled) window.setConnectionButtonsEnabled(false);\r\n\r\n            showToast('info', '正在断开设备...');\r\n            // --- Stop PTZ position polling ---\r\n            if (window.stopPtzPositionPoll) window.stopPtzPositionPoll();\r\n\r\n            // v6.54: 禁用主控台和高级功能\r\n            if (window.disableAllControls) window.disableAllControls('请先连接设备');\r\n\r\n            apiPost('/api/v1/devices/' + ip + '/disconnect', null).then(function() {\r\n                showToast('success', '设备已断开: ' + ip);\r\n                addLog('info', '设备已断开: ' + ip);\r\n                // --- Clear global window.connectedDevice first, before refresh ---\r\n                if (window.connectedDevice && window.connectedDevice.ip === ip) {\r\n                    window.connectedDevice = null;\r\n                    addLog('info', '已清除连接设备状态');\r\n                    // WASM SDK: 同步登出设备\r\n                    if (typeof onDeviceDisconnected === 'function') onDeviceDisconnected();\r\n                }\r\n                if (window.updateDeviceStatus) window.updateDeviceStatus();\r\n                refreshDevices();\r\n\n[1363 more lines in file. Use offset=1507 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1782851206118}}
