{"type":"message","id":"6b412b29","parentId":"33eca863","timestamp":"2026-06-30T20:26:52.761Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me check the `switchPage` function and the `loadDevicesQuick` function to understand issue 2.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"Now let me check the switchPage and loadDevicesQuick functions:\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_e6bf5170e691473ca4709dee","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":60,"offset":2533,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\index.html"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_546725a317b24cb4b42fb764","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":40,"offset":1160,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\index.html"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":6,"output":190,"cacheRead":35102,"cacheWrite":1550,"totalTokens":36848,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782851206119,"responseId":"msg_c053c608-87d2-43e3-94dd-0bca84c25ddf"}}
{"type":"message","id":"bf8b39be","parentId":"6b412b29","timestamp":"2026-06-30T20:26:52.870Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_e6bf5170e691473ca4709dee","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"    window.switchPage = function(page) {\r\n        document.querySelectorAll('.nav-btn').forEach(function(b) { b.classList.remove('active'); });\r\n        document.querySelectorAll('.page').forEach(function(p) { p.classList.remove('active'); });\r\n        document.querySelector('[data-page=\"' + page + '\"]').classList.add('active');\r\n        document.getElementById('page-' + page).classList.add('active');\r\n\r\n        // 切换到主控台时,如果已登录但未播放,开始预览(渲染)\r\n        if (page === 'console' && WasmPlayer && WasmPlayer.loggedIn && !WasmPlayer.playing) {\r\n            var channel = WasmPlayer.channel || 1;\r\n            var streamType = window._currentStreamType || 3;\r\n            wasmStartRealPlay(channel, streamType, true);\r\n        }\r\n        // 切换到设置页时加载路径配置\r\n        if (page === 'settings' && typeof loadStorageSettings === 'function') {\r\n            loadStorageSettings();\r\n        }\r\n    };\r\n\r\n    console.log('[GLOBAL v5.27] Functions ready');\r\n\r\n    // ================================================================\r\n    // WASM 播放器集成 - 使用 wasm-player.js 模块\r\n    // ================================================================\r\n\r\n    // 页面加载时初始化 WASM SDK\r\n    window.addEventListener('load', function() {\r\n        if (typeof wasmInit === 'function') {\r\n            wasmInit();\r\n            console.log('[MAIN] WASM SDK init triggered');\r\n        }\r\n    });\r\n\r\n    // WASM SDK 就绪后,监听容器尺寸变化\r\n    window.addEventListener('wasm:ready', function() {\r\n        console.log('[MAIN] WASM SDK ready, attaching ResizeObserver');\r\n        wasmObserveResize('divPlugin');\r\n        if (typeof updateMediaInputStatus === 'function') updateMediaInputStatus('connecting');\r\n\r\n        // 自动登录:如果设备已连接(ISAPI 已完成登录),WASM 自动登录\r\n        if (window.connectedDevice && window.connectedDevice.ip) {\r\n            console.log('[WASM] Device already connected, auto-login...');\r\n            var ip = window.connectedDevice.ip;\r\n            var port = window.connectedDevice.port || 80;\r\n            var username = window.connectedDevice.username || 'admin';\r\n            var password = window.connectedDevice.password || '';\r\n\r\n            wasmLogin(ip, port, username, password).then(function(result) {\r\n                console.log('[WASM] Auto-login result:', result);\r\n            }).catch(function(err) {\r\n                console.error('[WASM] Auto-login failed:', err);\r\n            });\r\n        }\r\n    });\r\n\r\n    // WASM 登录事件 → 更新媒体输入状态 + 操作日志\r\n    window.addEventListener('wasm:login', function(e) {\r\n        if (typeof updateMediaInputStatus === 'function') updateMediaInputStatus('connecting');\r\n        if (typeof operationLog === 'function') {\r\n            var dev = window.connectedDevice;\r\n            var name = dev ? (dev.name || dev.device_name || dev.ip) : (e.detail ? e.detail.ip : '设备');\r\n\n[277 more lines in file. Use offset=2593 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1782851212870}}
{"type":"message","id":"e6fb44ec","parentId":"bf8b39be","timestamp":"2026-06-30T20:26:52.871Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_546725a317b24cb4b42fb764","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"        function refreshDevices() {\r\n            console.log('[REFRESH] refreshDevices called');\r\n            var btn = document.getElementById('btnDiscover');\r\n            var spinner = document.getElementById('discoverSpinner');\r\n            if (spinner) spinner.style.display = 'inline-block';\r\n            return apiPost('/api/v1/devices/refresh', {}).then(function(result) {\r\n                console.log('[REFRESH] API response:', result);\r\n                if (spinner) spinner.style.display = 'none';\r\n                if (!result.success) {\r\n                    allDevices = [];\r\n                    renderDevices([]);\r\n                    return;\r\n                }\r\n                allDevices = result.data || [];\r\n                renderDevices(allDevices);\r\n                // Update dashboard counters\r\n                var online = allDevices.filter(function(d) { return d.status === '在线' || d.status === '已连接'; }).length;\r\n                var countEl = document.getElementById('devCount');\r\n                if (countEl) countEl.textContent = allDevices.length;\r\n                var onlineEl = document.getElementById('devOnline');\r\n                if (onlineEl) onlineEl.textContent = online;\r\n                var totalEl = document.getElementById('devTotal');\r\n                if (totalEl) totalEl.textContent = allDevices.length;\r\n                // Update PTZ & advanced device dropdowns\r\n                refreshPtzDeviceList();\r\n                refreshAdvancedDeviceSelectors();\r\n            }).catch(function(e) {\r\n                if (spinner) spinner.style.display = 'none';\r\n                console.warn('Failed to refresh devices:', e);\r\n            });\r\n        }\r\n        function loadDevicesQuick() {\r\n            // 快速获取设备列表（无状态，不ping）\r\n            return apiGet('/api/v1/devices').then(function(result) {\r\n                if (result.success) {\r\n                    allDevices = result.data || [];\r\n                    renderDevices(allDevices);\r\n                }\r\n            });\r\n        }\r\n\n[1670 more lines in file. Use offset=1200 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1782851212870}}
{"type":"message","id":"292d365c","parentId":"e6fb44ec","timestamp":"2026-06-30T20:26:57.407Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"...\n\nNow I have a clear picture. Let me also check the `renderDevices` function to understand how status is rendered:\n\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_8a97104c9904464cb50d13e3","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":60,"offset":1200,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\index.html"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_67cbe79c5c0349b2a393cf9a","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":60,"offset":380,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\index.html"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":6,"output":178,"cacheRead":35102,"cacheWrite":2835,"totalTokens":38121,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782851212871,"responseId":"msg_85e0972a-cd6b-40fc-8d05-529ae73ecdb2"}}
{"type":"message","id":"ed5fbb5d","parentId":"292d365c","timestamp":"2026-06-30T20:26:57.507Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_8a97104c9904464cb50d13e3","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"        function renderDevices(devices) {\r\n            var tb = document.getElementById('deviceTable');\r\n            if (!tb) return;\r\n            if (!devices.length) {\r\n                tb.innerHTML = '<tr><td colspan=\"7\" style=\"text-align:center;color:#6e7681\">暂无设备</td></tr>'; \r\n                return;\r\n            }\r\n            var html = devices.map(function(d) {\r\n                var statusBadge = d.status === '已连接'\r\n                    ? '<span class=\"badge online\">已连接</span>'\r\n                    : (d.status === '在线'\r\n                        ? '<span class=\"badge online\">在线</span>'\r\n                        : '<span class=\"badge offline\">离线</span>');\r\n                var actions = buildDeviceActions(d);\r\n                return '<tr>'\r\n                    + '<td>' + (d.mac || '--') + '</td>'\r\n                    + '<td>' + (d.ip || '--') + '</td>' \r\n                    + '<td>' + (d.gateway || '--') + '</td>' \r\n                    + '<td>' + (d.name || d.device_name || '--') + '</td>'\r\n                    + '<td>' + (d.model || '--') + '</td>' \r\n                    + '<td>' + statusBadge + '</td>'\r\n                    + '<td>' + actions + '</td>'\r\n                    + '</tr>';\r\n            }).join('');\r\n            tb.innerHTML = html;\r\n        }\r\n        function buildDeviceActions(d) {\r\n            var btns = [];\r\n            var isConnected = window.connectedDevice && window.connectedDevice.ip === d.ip;\r\n            // v6.35: 连接开关(只有一个设备可连接)\r\n            var switchHtml = '<label class=\"switch\"><input type=\"checkbox\" ' +\r\n                (isConnected ? 'checked' : '') + ' onchange=\"toggleDeviceConnect(\\'' + d.ip + '\\', this.checked, \\'' + (d.gateway || '') + '\\')\" /><span class=\"slider\"></span></label>';\r\n            btns.push(switchHtml);\r\n            // v6.35: 信息按钮(弹窗显示设备详情)\r\n            btns.push('<button class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" onclick=\"showDeviceInfoModal(\\'' + d.ip + '\\')\">信息</button>');\r\n            // Add modify IP button for all devices\r\n            // v7.15: 添加/删除按钮交互式\r\n            var isAdded = d.has_credentials;\r\n            if (isAdded) {\r\n                btns.push('<button class=\"btn btn-danger btn-sm\" onclick=\"deleteDevice(\\'' + (d.mac || d.ip) + '\\')\">删除</button>');\r\n            } else {\r\n                btns.push('<button class=\"btn btn-primary btn-sm\" onclick=\"quickAddDevice(\\'' + d.ip + '\\', \\'' + (d.gateway || '') + '\\')\">添加</button>');\r\n            }\r\n            return '<div class=\"actions\" style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px\">' + btns.join('') + '</div>';\r\n        }\r\n        // v6.35: 切换设备连接状态\r\n        window.toggleDeviceConnect = function(ip, checked, gateway) {\r\n            if (checked) {\r\n                var d = allDevices.find(function(dev) { return dev.ip === ip; });\r\n                if (d && d.has_credentials) {\r\n                    connectDevice(ip);\r\n                } else {\r\n                    showQuickAddModal(ip, gateway);\r\n                }\r\n            } else {\r\n                disconnectDevice(ip);\r\n            }\r\n        };\r\n        // v7.15: 快速添加设备\r\n        window.quickAddDevice = function(ip, gateway) {\r\n\n[1610 more lines in file. Use offset=1260 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1782851217507}}
{"type":"message","id":"85be3747","parentId":"ed5fbb5d","timestamp":"2026-06-30T20:26:57.507Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_67cbe79c5c0349b2a393cf9a","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"            console.log('[INIT] init() called');\r\n            updateClock();\r\n            setInterval(updateClock, 1000);\r\n            initNav();\r\n            initPtzSpeed();\r\n            initMouseUp();\r\n            loadDevicesQuick();\r\n            // v6.0: 从后端获取连接状态\r\n            restoreConnectionState();\r\n            addLog('info', 'AstroHub 已启动');\r\n            connectWS();\r\n            loadLocalhostInfo();\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        // v7.15: 加载本机信息\r\n        function loadLocalhostInfo() {\r\n            apiGet('/api/v1/localhost').then(function(result) {\r\n                if (result.success && result.data) {\r\n                    var info = result.data;\r\n                    document.getElementById('localhost-hostname').textContent = info.hostname || '-';\r\n                    document.getElementById('localhost-cpu').textContent = info.cpu_model || '-';\r\n                    document.getElementById('localhost-ram').textContent = info.ram_gb ? info.ram_gb + ' GB' : '-';\r\n                    var gpu = (info.gpu_names || []).join(', ') || '-';\r\n                    if (info.vram_gb > 0) gpu += ' (' + info.vram_gb + 'GB)';\r\n                    document.getElementById('localhost-gpu').textContent = gpu;\r\n                    document.getElementById('localhost-ip').textContent = info.local_ip || '-';\r\n                    document.getElementById('localhost-gateway').textContent = info.gateway || '-';\r\n                    window.localhostGateway = info.gateway; // 保存网关供后续使用\r\n                    document.getElementById('localhostCard').style.display = 'block';\r\n\r\n                    // v7.15: 首次运行,显示提示并重启\r\n                    if (result.first_run) {\r\n                        showStartupProgress();\r\n                    }\r\n                }\r\n            }).catch(function(e) { console.warn('加载本机信息失败:', e); });\r\n        }\r\n        // v7.15: 显示启动进度条\r\n\r\n        // v7.117: 统一弹窗组件 - 替代所有旧弹窗\r\n        // options: { type:'alert'|'confirm'|'form', title, message, fields, onConfirm, onCancel }\r\n        window.showModal = function(options) {\r\n            closeModal();\r\n            var opts = options || {};\r\n            var type = opts.type || 'alert';\r\n            var title = opts.title || (type === 'confirm' ? '确认' : '提示');\r\n            var titleColor = type === 'confirm' ? '#58a6ff' : '#f0883e';\r\n            var bodyHtml = '';\r\n\r\n            if (type === 'form' && opts.fields) {\r\n                opts.fields.forEach(function(f) {\r\n                    bodyHtml += '<div class=\"astro-modal-field\"><label>' + (f.label || '') + '</label>' +\r\n                        '<input type=\"' + (f.type || 'text') + '\" id=\"astroModalField_' + (f.id || '') + '\"' +\r\n                        ' value=\"' + (f.value || '') + '\" placeholder=\"' + (f.placeholder || '') + '\"' +\r\n                        (f.required ? ' required' : '') + '></div>';\r\n                });\r\n            } else if (opts.message) {\r\n                bodyHtml = '<p class=\"astro-modal-body\">' + opts.message + '</p>';\r\n            }\r\n\r\n\n[2430 more lines in file. Use offset=440 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1782851217507}}
{"type":"message","id":"5af6ff59","parentId":"85be3747","timestamp":"2026-06-30T20:27:16.636Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a clear picture of all three issues. Let me summarize and present the fix plan:\n\n**Issue 1: 连接/断开没有成功提示**\n- `connectDevice()` line 1331: `showToast('info', '正在连接设备...')` ✅ 有\n- 连接成功后 line 1412 area: Let me check if there's a success toast...\n\nActually looking at the grep results:\n- line 1412: `showToast('success', '设备已连接: ' + ip);` ✅\n- line 1496: `showToast('success', '设备已断开: ' + ip);` ✅\n\n\n- The disconnect function at line 1496 also shows a success toast after the API call completes, so that's working. But I need to trace through the actual flow more carefully—the user says there are no success notifications, so something must be preventing these toasts from displaying.\n\nLet me examine what happens after the connect and disconnect API responses come back. Looking at the connect flow starting around line 1322, it shows an initial \"connecting...\" toast, then makes the API call. When successful, it should hit line 1412 with the success toast, but I need to verify the entire code path to see if there's something blocking that toast from appearing.\n\nActually, I should check if the issue is specifically with the top quick-connect button versus the device page connect button—the user mentioned both the top bar quick connect and the device page connect button. Let me trace through how the dashboard quick connect works and whether it's using the same `connectDevice()` function or a different code path that might not have the toast notification.\n\nThe real problem I'm seeing is that when switching to the devices page, `loadDevicesQuick()` is called at line 612, which fetches from `GET /devices` without pinging the devices, so they all show as offline. This needs to be changed to `refreshDevices()` which calls `POST /devices/refresh` to get actual status. But wait, the user already specified this should only happen when switching pages, so I need to reconsider what the actual issue is here.\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"好了老板，三个问题我都分析完了，以下是修复计划：\n\n---\n\n## 修复计划\n\n### 问题1：连接/断开无成功提示\n\n**现状**：代码中有 `showToast('success', '设备已连接')` 和 `showToast('success', '设备已断开')`，逻辑正确。\n\n**需排查**：\n- 顶部快速连接入口 → 调用的也是 `connectDevice(ip)`，理论上会触发\n- 可能是 toast 被后续操作覆盖（如 `refreshDevices` 后的其他 toast）\n- 或 toast 显示时间太短\n\n**修复**：检查 toast 持续时间，确保连接/断开成功 toast 不被覆盖，延长显示时间（3→5秒）。\n\n---\n\n### 问题2：切换到设备管理页不刷新状态\n\n**根因已确认**：\n\n```\nswitchPage('devices') → 调用 loadDevicesQuick()\n                        ↓\n                  GET /devices（无ping，不返回 status）\n                        ↓\n                  渲染时 d.status = undefined → 显示\"离线\"\n```\n\n**修复**：切换到设备页面时，先 `loadDevicesQuick()` 立即显示表格，然后同时触发一次 `refreshDevices()` 异步获取真实状态。\n\n---\n\n### 问题3：列顺序调整\n\n**当前顺序**：\n```\nMAC | IP | 网关 | 名称 | 型号 | 状态 | 操作\n```\n\n**目标顺序**：\n```\n序号 | 设备型号 | 设备名称 | MAC | IP地址 | 网关地址 | 状态 | 操作\n```\n\n**涉及修改**：\n- `devices.html` — `<thead>` 表头\n- `index.html` — `renderDevices()` 函数中的列渲染顺序\n- 新增序号列（`i+1`）\n\n---\n\n### 涉及文件\n\n| 文件 | 改动 |\n|------|------|\n| `src/web/includes/devices.html` | 表头列顺序 |\n| `src/web/index.html` | `renderDevices()` 列顺序 + 序号；`switchPage` 增加 refreshDevices 调用；toast 持续时间 |\n\n等你评审。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":6,"output":935,"cacheRead":35102,"cacheWrite":4553,"totalTokens":40596,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782851217508,"responseId":"msg_8a8c4816-6365-4d42-877d-3991cee77e27"}}
