{"type":"message","id":"c8d4bfd0","parentId":"5e950350","timestamp":"2026-06-30T20:32:25.556Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要求执行修改，备份已完成。现在需要修改三个问题：\n\n1. 连接/断开无成功提示 - 需要检查showToast的持续时间，可能是被覆盖或显示时间太短\n2. 切换到设备管理页不刷新状态 - switchPage调用loadDevicesQuick()而不是refreshDevices()\n3. 列顺序调整 - devices.html表头 + renderDevices()函数\n\n让我先检查showToast函数，看看持续时间设置。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_4eead22441324658b049c025","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":30,"offset":1070,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\index.html"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":6,"output":171,"cacheRead":40794,"cacheWrite":238,"totalTokens":41209,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782851540387,"responseId":"msg_78eef49a-0ca2-44f4-9fe7-84a29bb203ca"}}
{"type":"message","id":"4ba2cee3","parentId":"c8d4bfd0","timestamp":"2026-06-30T20:32:25.604Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_4eead22441324658b049c025","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"        function showToast(type, message) {\r\n            var container = document.getElementById('toastContainer');\r\n            var toast = document.createElement('div');\r\n            toast.className = 'toast ' + type + ' show';  // v7.39: 添加 show class\r\n            toast.textContent = message;\r\n            container.appendChild(toast);\r\n            setTimeout(function() {\r\n                toast.classList.remove('show');\r\n                setTimeout(function() {\r\n                    if (toast.parentNode) toast.parentNode.removeChild(toast);\r\n                }, 300);\r\n            }, 3700);\r\n        }\r\n        // Logging\r\n        function addLog(level, msg) {\r\n            var c = document.getElementById('logContainer');\r\n            if (!c) return;\r\n            var d = document.createElement('div');\r\n            d.className = 'log-entry ' + level;\r\n            d.textContent = '[' + new Date().toLocaleTimeString() + '] ' + msg;\r\n            c.insertBefore(d, c.firstChild);\r\n            if (c.children.length > 50) c.removeChild(c.lastChild);\r\n        }\r\n        // WebSocket\r\n        function connectWS() {\r\n            try {\r\n                var ws = new WebSocket(WS_URL);\r\n                ws.onopen = function() {\r\n                    addLog('info', 'WebSocket 已连接');\r\n                };\r\n\n[1770 more lines in file. Use offset=1100 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1782851545604}}
{"type":"message","id":"d4a2f948","parentId":"4ba2cee3","timestamp":"2026-06-30T20:32:40.371Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to execute the fixes. I already:\n1. Read the connectDevice, disconnectDevice, showToast, refreshDevices, loadDevicesQuick, switchPage, renderDevices, and buildDeviceActions functions.\n2. Backed up the files.\n\nNow I need to make three changes:\n\n**Issue 1: Toast duration for connect/disconnect**\nCurrent: 3700ms display time. The user says no success notification is shown. Let me check - the showToast function exists and connectDevice does call `showToast('success', '设备已连接: ' + ip)`. But the user says it doesn't show. \n \nLet me trace through the connectDevice flow more carefully to see if there's a code path where the success toast never actually gets triggered. The function shows an info toast when connecting starts, then calls the API, but I need to verify whether the success toast is actually being reached in the response handler. I'm looking at the disconnect flow and seeing where the toast should fire, but the user's complaint is that no success messages appear when connecting or disconnecting devices. Let me trace through the connectDevice function more carefully to see if the success toast is actually being reached or if there's an early return preventing it. I need to verify whether the success toast is actually being triggered at that line. Looking back at the grep output, I can see the pattern matches for `showToast` calls, but the line numbers seem off compared to what I'm reading in the file. Let me search more carefully to confirm whether line 1412 really contains the success message or if the actual call is elsewhere in the code.\n 让我再仔细查看 connectDevice 的完整流程：\n\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_f1767289fa374640a2b4ba9c","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":100,"offset":1322,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\index.html"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_76ffd7e60a5b4dbaa4f71c4d","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":40,"offset":1477,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\index.html"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_0409e3d369aa41f1bfecbf80","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":30,"offset":1191,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\index.html"}},{"type":"text","text":"\n</think>\n\nToast 显示3700ms。问题1可能是连接成功后紧接着调用了 refreshDevices/其他操作导致 toast 被新的覆盖。现在执行三个修复。Now let me also check the exact connect success flow to understand what happens after showToast success:\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_ca9cccf2a65347f3a9d0503e","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":30,"offset":1390,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\index.html"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":6,"output":707,"cacheRead":41032,"cacheWrite":482,"totalTokens":42227,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782851545605,"responseId":"msg_3df989b2-d503-4339-acd8-98070acd924c"}}
{"type":"message","id":"46bb94b7","parentId":"d4a2f948","timestamp":"2026-06-30T20:32:40.500Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_f1767289fa374640a2b4ba9c","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"        function connectDevice(ip) {\r\n            // v6.54: 防止重复点击\r\n            if (_connectionOperationInProgress) {\r\n                showToast('warning', '请等待上一次操作完成');\r\n                return;\r\n            }\r\n            _connectionOperationInProgress = true;\r\n\r\n            addLog('info', '正在连接设备: ' + ip);\r\n            showToast('info', '正在连接设备...');\r\n\r\n            // 禁用连接按钮\r\n            if (window.setConnectionButtonsEnabled) window.setConnectionButtonsEnabled(false);\r\n\r\n            // 先获取 credentials\r\n            apiGet('/api/v1/ptz/devices/' + ip + '/credentials').then(function(creds) {\r\n                var username = (creds && creds.success) ? creds.username : 'admin';\r\n                var password = (creds && creds.success) ? creds.password : '';\r\n                var port = (creds && creds.success) ? (creds.port || 80) : 80;\r\n\r\n                // 再调用 connect API\r\n                apiPost('/api/v1/devices/' + ip + '/connect', { username: username, password: password, port: port }).then(function(result) {\r\n                    if (result && result.success) {\r\n                        addLog('success', result.message || '连接成功');\r\n                        // Set connectedDevice BEFORE refreshDevices\r\n                        var dev = allDevices.find(function(d) { return d.ip === ip; }) || { ip: ip };\r\n                        window.connectedDevice = {\r\n                            ip: dev.ip, model: dev.model || '', name: dev.name || '', device_name: dev.device_name || '',\r\n                            mac: dev.mac || '', username: username, password: password, port: port, online: true\r\n                        };\r\n                        // Update button immediately\r\n                        if (window.updateDeviceStatus) window.updateDeviceStatus();\r\n                        // v7.31: 连接成功后立即启用所有控件\r\n                        if (window.enableAllControls) window.enableAllControls();\r\n                        // WASM SDK: 同步登录设备\r\n                        if (typeof onDeviceConnected === 'function') onDeviceConnected();\r\n                        // 动态加载设备图像参数(白平衡、快门、光圈、降噪、锐度、OSD)\r\n                        // v5.42: 增加延迟确保设备连接完成\r\n                        setTimeout(function() {\r\n                            console.log('[CONNECT] Calling loadDeviceImageParams for:', ip);\r\n                            if (typeof loadDeviceImageParams === 'function') {\r\n                                loadDeviceImageParams(ip);\r\n                                console.log('[CONNECT] loadDeviceImageParams called');\r\n                            } else {\r\n                                console.error('[CONNECT] loadDeviceImageParams not found');\r\n                            }\r\n                            // 加载对焦模式\r\n                            if (typeof loadFocusMode === 'function') {\r\n                                loadFocusMode();\r\n                            }\r\n                        }, 500);\r\n                        // v6.54: 等待视频播放后启用按钮\r\n                        setTimeout(function() {\r\n                            _connectionOperationInProgress = false;\r\n                            if (window.setConnectionButtonsEnabled) window.setConnectionButtonsEnabled(true);\r\n                        }, 3000);\r\n                    } else if (result && result.message && result.message.indexOf('凭证') >= 0) {\r\n                        // credentials 错误,提示用户输入\r\n                        _connectionOperationInProgress = false;\r\n                        if (window.setConnectionButtonsEnabled) window.setConnectionButtonsEnabled(true);\r\n                        showModal({\r\n                            type:'form',\r\n                            title:'输入凭证',\r\n                            fields:[\r\n                                {id:'credUser',label:'用户名',value:'admin'},\r\n                                {id:'credPass',label:'密码',type:'password',value:'',required:true}\r\n                            ],\r\n                            onConfirm:function(data){\r\n                                var u=(data.credUser||'').trim()||'admin';\r\n                                var p=data.credPass;\r\n                                if(!p)return;\r\n                                connectDeviceWithCreds(ip,u,p,80);\r\n                            }\r\n                        });\r\n                    } else {\r\n                        _connectionOperationInProgress = false;\r\n                        if (window.setConnectionButtonsEnabled) window.setConnectionButtonsEnabled(true);\r\n                        showToast('error', result ? result.message : '连接失败');\r\n                        addLog('error', result ? result.message : '连接失败');\r\n                    }\r\n                }).catch(function(e) {\r\n                    _connectionOperationInProgress = false;\r\n                    if (window.setConnectionButtonsEnabled) window.setConnectionButtonsEnabled(true);\r\n                    showToast('error', '连接异常: ' + e.message);\r\n                    addLog('error', '连接异常: ' + e.message);\r\n                });\r\n            }).catch(function(e) {\r\n                // credentials API 失败,尝试无密码连接\r\n                apiPost('/api/v1/devices/' + ip + '/connect', null).then(function(result) {\r\n                    if (result && result.success) {\r\n                        showToast('success', '设备已连接: ' + ip);\r\n                        refreshDevices();\r\n                        refreshPtzDeviceList();\r\n                        refreshAdvancedDeviceSelectors();\r\n                        var dev = allDevices.find(function(d) { return d.ip === ip; });\r\n                        if (dev) {\r\n                            window.connectedDevice = {\r\n                                ip: dev.ip, model: dev.model || '', name: dev.name || '', device_name: dev.device_name || '',\r\n                                mac: dev.mac || '', username: 'admin', password: '', port: 80, online: true\r\n                            };\r\n\n[1448 more lines in file. Use offset=1422 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1782851560500}}
{"type":"message","id":"5015fe0f","parentId":"46bb94b7","timestamp":"2026-06-30T20:32:40.500Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_76ffd7e60a5b4dbaa4f71c4d","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"        function disconnectDevice(ip) {\r\n            // v6.54: 防止重复点击\r\n            if (_connectionOperationInProgress) {\r\n                showToast('warning', '请等待上一次操作完成');\r\n                return;\r\n            }\r\n            _connectionOperationInProgress = true;\r\n\r\n            // 禁用连接按钮\r\n            if (window.setConnectionButtonsEnabled) window.setConnectionButtonsEnabled(false);\r\n\r\n            showToast('info', '正在断开设备...');\r\n            // --- Stop PTZ position polling ---\r\n            if (window.stopPtzPositionPoll) window.stopPtzPositionPoll();\r\n\r\n            // v6.54: 禁用主控台和高级功能\r\n            if (window.disableAllControls) window.disableAllControls('请先连接设备');\r\n\r\n            apiPost('/api/v1/devices/' + ip + '/disconnect', null).then(function() {\r\n                showToast('success', '设备已断开: ' + ip);\r\n                addLog('info', '设备已断开: ' + ip);\r\n                // --- Clear global window.connectedDevice first, before refresh ---\r\n                if (window.connectedDevice && window.connectedDevice.ip === ip) {\r\n                    window.connectedDevice = null;\r\n                    addLog('info', '已清除连接设备状态');\r\n                    // WASM SDK: 同步登出设备\r\n                    if (typeof onDeviceDisconnected === 'function') onDeviceDisconnected();\r\n                }\r\n                if (window.updateDeviceStatus) window.updateDeviceStatus();\r\n                refreshDevices();\r\n                refreshPtzDeviceList();\r\n                refreshAdvancedDeviceSelectors();\r\n                var panel = document.getElementById('deviceInfoPanel');\r\n                if (panel) panel.style.display = 'none';\r\n\r\n                _connectionOperationInProgress = false;\r\n                if (window.setConnectionButtonsEnabled) window.setConnectionButtonsEnabled(true);\r\n            }).catch(function(e) {\r\n                _connectionOperationInProgress = false;\r\n                if (window.setConnectionButtonsEnabled) window.setConnectionButtonsEnabled(true);\r\n\n[1353 more lines in file. Use offset=1517 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1782851560500}}
{"type":"message","id":"5eca5026","parentId":"5015fe0f","timestamp":"2026-06-30T20:32:40.500Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_0409e3d369aa41f1bfecbf80","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"        function loadDevicesQuick() {\r\n            // 快速获取设备列表（无状态，不ping）\r\n            return apiGet('/api/v1/devices').then(function(result) {\r\n                if (result.success) {\r\n                    allDevices = result.data || [];\r\n                    renderDevices(allDevices);\r\n                }\r\n            });\r\n        }\r\n        function renderDevices(devices) {\r\n            var tb = document.getElementById('deviceTable');\r\n            if (!tb) return;\r\n            if (!devices.length) {\r\n                tb.innerHTML = '<tr><td colspan=\"7\" style=\"text-align:center;color:#6e7681\">暂无设备</td></tr>'; \r\n                return;\r\n            }\r\n            var html = devices.map(function(d) {\r\n                var statusBadge = d.status === '已连接'\r\n                    ? '<span class=\"badge online\">已连接</span>'\r\n                    : (d.status === '在线'\r\n                        ? '<span class=\"badge online\">在线</span>'\r\n                        : '<span class=\"badge offline\">离线</span>');\r\n                var actions = buildDeviceActions(d);\r\n                return '<tr>'\r\n                    + '<td>' + (d.mac || '--') + '</td>'\r\n                    + '<td>' + (d.ip || '--') + '</td>' \r\n                    + '<td>' + (d.gateway || '--') + '</td>' \r\n                    + '<td>' + (d.name || d.device_name || '--') + '</td>'\r\n                    + '<td>' + (d.model || '--') + '</td>' \r\n                    + '<td>' + statusBadge + '</td>'\r\n\n[1649 more lines in file. Use offset=1221 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1782851560500}}
{"type":"message","id":"63984a24","parentId":"5eca5026","timestamp":"2026-06-30T20:32:40.501Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_ca9cccf2a65347f3a9d0503e","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"                                var u=(data.credUser||'').trim()||'admin';\r\n                                var p=data.credPass;\r\n                                if(!p)return;\r\n                                connectDeviceWithCreds(ip,u,p,80);\r\n                            }\r\n                        });\r\n                    } else {\r\n                        _connectionOperationInProgress = false;\r\n                        if (window.setConnectionButtonsEnabled) window.setConnectionButtonsEnabled(true);\r\n                        showToast('error', result ? result.message : '连接失败');\r\n                        addLog('error', result ? result.message : '连接失败');\r\n                    }\r\n                }).catch(function(e) {\r\n                    _connectionOperationInProgress = false;\r\n                    if (window.setConnectionButtonsEnabled) window.setConnectionButtonsEnabled(true);\r\n                    showToast('error', '连接异常: ' + e.message);\r\n                    addLog('error', '连接异常: ' + e.message);\r\n                });\r\n            }).catch(function(e) {\r\n                // credentials API 失败,尝试无密码连接\r\n                apiPost('/api/v1/devices/' + ip + '/connect', null).then(function(result) {\r\n                    if (result && result.success) {\r\n                        showToast('success', '设备已连接: ' + ip);\r\n                        refreshDevices();\r\n                        refreshPtzDeviceList();\r\n                        refreshAdvancedDeviceSelectors();\r\n                        var dev = allDevices.find(function(d) { return d.ip === ip; });\r\n                        if (dev) {\r\n                            window.connectedDevice = {\r\n                                ip: dev.ip, model: dev.model || '', name: dev.name || '', device_name: dev.device_name || '',\r\n\n[1450 more lines in file. Use offset=1420 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1782851560500}}
{"type":"message","id":"ddfbd998","parentId":"63984a24","timestamp":"2026-06-30T20:32:51.469Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"...\n\nNow I can see the full picture. Let me also check the `connectDeviceWithCreds` function to see if it has the same issue.\n\nLooking at the code:\n\n**Issue 1: 连接/断开无成功提示**\n\nThe problem is in the **main success path** of `connectDevice()` (lines 1342-1380):\n- When `result.success` is true, it calls `addLog('success', result.message || '连接成功')` but **NO `showToast('success', ...)`**!\n- The `showToast('success', '设备已连接: ' + ip)` is only in the **fallback path** (credentials API 失败, line ~1412).\n\n\n- So the main connect path never shows a toast notification, while the disconnect path correctly calls `showToast('success', '设备已断开: ' + ip)`.\n\nThe fix is straightforward: I need to add the missing `showToast` call in the main success path of `connectDevice()`.\n\n**Issue 2: 切换到设备管理页不刷新状态**\n\nThe `switchPage('devices')` function doesn't exist yet in the code.  When navigating to the devices page, it only calls `loadDevicesQuick()` which makes a GET request without pinging, so devices show as offline. I need to add a call to `refreshDevices()` after the initial load to get the actual status.\n\n**Issue 3: 列顺序**\n\nThe current table columns are in the wrong order. I need to rearrange them from MAC | IP | 网关 | 名称 | 型号 | 状态 | 操作 to 序号 | 设备型号 | 设备名称 | MAC | IP地址 | 网关地址 | 状态 | 操作, which requires updating both the table header in devices.html and the corresponding data columns.\n\nNow I'm checking `connectDeviceWithCreds` to verify if it has the same issue.\n...","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"Let me also check `connectDeviceWithCreds`:\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_ed3c4b1b47e541129eff2e46","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":40,"offset":1438,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\index.html"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":6,"output":508,"cacheRead":41514,"cacheWrite":3040,"totalTokens":45068,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782851560501,"responseId":"msg_bc31a58a-b378-4928-bade-022c00fd2b8e"}}
{"type":"message","id":"7e3cb18b","parentId":"ddfbd998","timestamp":"2026-06-30T20:32:51.577Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_ed3c4b1b47e541129eff2e46","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"        function connectDeviceWithCreds(ip, username, password, port) {\r\n            apiPost('/api/v1/devices/' + ip + '/connect', {\r\n                username: username, password: password, port: port\r\n            }).then(function(result) {\r\n                if (result && result.success) {\r\n                    showToast('success', '设备已连接: ' + ip);\r\n                    addLog('success', result.message || '连接成功');\r\n                    refreshDevices();\r\n                    refreshPtzDeviceList();\r\n                    refreshAdvancedDeviceSelectors();\r\n                    // --- v3: Update global window.connectedDevice ---\r\n                    var dev = allDevices.find(function(d) { return d.ip === ip; });\r\n                    if (dev) {\r\n                        window.connectedDevice = window.connectedDevice = {\r\n                            ip: dev.ip, model: dev.model || '', name: dev.name || '', device_name: dev.device_name || '',\r\n                            mac: dev.mac || '', username: username, password: password, port: port, online: true\r\n                        };\r\n                        addLog('info', '已连接设备: ' + window.connectedDevice.ip);\r\n                        // v7.31: 连接成功后启用所有控件\r\n                        if (window.enableAllControls) window.enableAllControls();\r\n                        // 动态加载设备图像参数\r\n                        setTimeout(function() {\r\n                            console.log('[CONNECT2] Calling loadDeviceImageParams for:', ip);\r\n                            if (typeof loadDeviceImageParams === 'function') {\r\n                                loadDeviceImageParams(ip);\r\n                            }\r\n                        }, 500);\r\n                        // v7.57: 连接成功后启用控件\r\n                        if (window.updateDeviceStatus) window.updateDeviceStatus();\r\n                        // WASM SDK: 同步登录设备\r\n                        if (typeof onDeviceConnected === 'function') onDeviceConnected();\r\n                    }\r\n                } else {\r\n                    showToast('error', result ? result.message : '连接失败');\r\n                }\r\n            }).catch(function(e) {\r\n                showToast('error', '连接异常: ' + e.message);\r\n            });\r\n        }\r\n        function disconnectDevice(ip) {\r\n\n[1392 more lines in file. Use offset=1478 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1782851571577}}
{"type":"message","id":"0d7e5f75","parentId":"7e3cb18b","timestamp":"2026-06-30T20:33:04.993Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK, now I have a clear picture of all three issues:\n\n**Issue 1: 连接/断开无成功提示**\n\nLooking at `connectDevice(ip)` main success path (when credentials API succeeds and connect succeeds):\n- Line ~1349: `addLog('success', result.message || '连接成功');` - only logs, no showToast!\n- The `showToast('success', '设备已连接: ' + ip)` is only in:\n  - `connectDeviceWithCreds` (line 1443) ✅\n  - fallback path when credentials API fails (line ~1412) ✅\n  \nThe main success path in `connectDevice()` is missing the toast notification. I need to add it there.\n\nFor `disconnectDevice`, the toast appears at line 1496 before `refreshDevices()` is called at line 1506, so the timing should work correctly. But if the user isn't seeing any success messages at all, there might be something else preventing the toast from displaying. Looking at the main connect path, I see it's missing the success toast notification entirely—that's the bug. The disconnect flow properly shows a toast and then refreshes, so the connect should do the same before calling `refreshDevices()` to avoid overwriting the notification.\n\nNow I'm identifying the specific fixes needed: the `connectDevice()` function requires a success toast, the page switching logic needs to call `refreshDevices()` instead of just `loadDevicesQuick()` for the devices page, and the devices table needs column reordering to match the new structure with device model, name, MAC, IP, gateway, status, and actions. I should also update the colspan value to reflect the correct number of columns.\n\nImplementing all three fixes...\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"根因分析完成。开始修改。\n\n**问题1根因**：`connectDevice()` 主路径（credentials获取成功→连接成功）缺少 `showToast('success', ...)`，只有 fallback 路径（credentials API失败→无密码连接）有。\n\n**问题2根因**：`switchPage('devices')` 只调用 `loadDevicesQuick()`（无ping），不触发状态刷新。\n\n**问题3**：列顺序调整。现在执行修改：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_948eadd3354e44228f246561","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"                    if (result && result.success) {\n                        showToast('success', '设备已连接: ' + ip);\n                        addLog('success', result.message || '连接成功');\n                        // Set connectedDevice BEFORE refreshDevices","oldText":"                    if (result && result.success) {\n                        addLog('success', result.message || '连接成功');\n                        // Set connectedDevice BEFORE refreshDevices"}],"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\index.html"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":6,"output":634,"cacheRead":41514,"cacheWrite":4025,"totalTokens":46179,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782851571578,"responseId":"msg_8ba02ff3-7da8-4c9e-a092-baaa1410f151"}}
