{"type":"message","id":"8961f188","parentId":"0cf0e9ea","timestamp":"2026-06-30T20:33:17.274Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to continue with the remaining fixes. Let me now fix issue 2 (switchPage to devices page should refresh) and issue 3 (column reorder).\n\nFor issue 2, I need to modify the switchPage function. Looking at the code:\n\n```javascript\n// In initNav or similar:\nif (btn.getAttribute('data-page') === 'devices') { loadDevicesQuick(); }\n```\n\nAnd the switchPage function at line 2533:\n```javascript\nwindow.switchPage = function(page) {\n    // ...\n    // 切换到主控台时,如果已登录但未播放,开始预览(渲染)\n\n\n```\n\nI need to add logic to the switchPage function that triggers a refreshDevices call when switching to the devices page, since the current code only calls loadDevicesQuick which doesn't get the latest device status.\n\nLooking at the flow: when the user navigates to the devices page, switchPage is called but it doesn't handle the refresh. I should add a case for when page === 'devices' that calls refreshDevices().\n\nI also need to update the renderDevices function to match the new column order with 序号, 设备型号, and 设备名称, and update the table headers in devices.html accordingly. The colspan for the empty state message needs to change from 7 to 8 to account for the additional column.\n\n```\n\njavascript\nwindow.switchPage = function(page) {\n    ...\n    // 切换到设置页时加载路径配置\n    if (page === 'settings' && typeof loadStorageSettings === 'function') {\n        loadStorageSettings();\n    }\n    // Add this:\n    if (page === 'devices') {\n        refreshDevices();\n    }\n};\n```\n\nLet me apply all three fixes now.\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"修复1完成。继续修复2和3：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_fb7739af085f4fa5a6de8f6c","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"        // 切换到设置页时加载路径配置\n        if (page === 'settings' && typeof loadStorageSettings === 'function') {\n            load