{"type":"message","id":"0eb29865","parentId":"ccac815e","timestamp":"2026-06-30T20:51:24.351Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户确认版本已更新到 v7.122。现在我需要验证三个修复是否生效：\n1. 连接/断开设备时显示成功提示\n2. 切换到设备管理页面时自动刷新状态\n3. 表格列顺序已调整\n\n让我截图验证这些修改。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"v7.122 确认 ✅\n\n截图验证修改：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_4354ec144b934845bfd348a2","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"import os\nos.environ['PYTHONDONTWRITEBYTECODE'] = '1'\n\nfrom playwright.sync_api import sync_playwright\nimport time\n\nurl = 'http://localhost:10280'\n\nwith sync_playwright() as p:\n    browser = p.chromium.launch(headless=True)\n    page = browser.new_page(viewport={'width': 1920, 'height': 1080})\n    page.goto(url)\n    time.sleep(2)\n    \n    # 点击设备管理页面\n    page.click('button[data-page=\"devices\"]')\n    time.sleep(3)\n    \n    # 截图验证列顺序和状态显示\n    page.screenshot(path='test_v7122_devices.png')\n    \n    print('截图已保存: test_v7122_devices.png')\n    \n    browser.close()\n","path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\test_v7122_verify.py"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_e5d067b86a5d407a98cdb281","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub; python test_v7122_verify.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":6,"output":379,"cacheRead":51821,"cacheWrite":254,"totalTokens":52460,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782852674622,"responseId":"msg_b4dcb197-f34d-4e89-9b09-d7d010756a29"}}
