{"type":"message","id":"e20c8896","parentId":"8bd1a2af","timestamp":"2026-06-30T21:07:17.465Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"D盘上的 AstroHub 相关目录：\n\n| 路径 | 类型 | 最后修改 |\n|------|------|---------|\n| `D:\\astrohub_backup_20260614` | **备份目录** | 2026/6/14 |\n| `D:\\astrohub_git_check` | Git 检查副本 | 2026/6/20 |\n| `D:\\PY APP\\Astro_hub\\astrohub` | **主开发目录** | 2026/6/21 |\n| `D:\\PY APP\\Astro_hub\\m1_ptz_astro` | M1 项目 | 2026/5/2 |\n\n### 备份命名规范\n\n```\nD:\\astrohub_backup_YYYYMMDD\n```\n\n- **前缀**: `astrohub_backup_`\n- **日期格式**: `YYYYMMDD`（8位纯数字）\n- **示例**: `D:\\astrohub_backup_20260614`\n\n### 备份内容结构\n\n```\nD:\\astrohub_backup_20260614/\n├── src/            # 源代码（advanced/api/ascom/core/ptz/web/等）\n├── config/         # 配置文件\n├── doc/            # 文档\n├── log/            # 日志\n├── review/         # 代码审查\n├── .gitignore\n├── start.bat / stop.bat\n├── *.md            # 各类文档（changelog/dev_notes/frontend_spec等）\n├── *.csv           # M1 方法提取数据\n└── __pycache__/\n```\n\n这是2026年6月14日的完整项目快照备份。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":6,"output":398,"cacheRead":72080,"cacheWrite":424,"totalTokens":72908,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782853622156,"responseId":"msg_3c05075c-a164-4701-a3ca-86c3d4ab5944"}}
